o-a-mans-home-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692957409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e867df52bc2d001991db2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-shows-moment-a-california-bear-opens-the-door-to-a-mans-home-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20video%2C%20captured%20by%20a%20digital%20doorbell%2C%20shows%20a%20bear%20followed%20by%20a%20cub%20enquiringly%20opening%20the%20door%20of%20a%20house%20in%20Half%20Moon%20Bay.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Marianne%20Guenot)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-shows-moment-a-california-bear-opens-the-door-to-a-mans-home-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAI%20Can%20Be%20Source%20Of%20Jobs%2C%20Must%20Be%20In%20Human%20Control%26quot%3B%3A%20Microsoft%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArtificial%20Intelligence%2C%20or%20AI%2C%20can%20be%20a%20source%20of%20growth%20-%20contrary%20to%20opinions%20it%20could%20cost%20millions%20their%20jobs%20-%20and%20will%20be%20as%20important%20to%20the%20future%20of%20knowledge%20as%20the%20invention%20of%20the%20printing%20press%20was%2C%20Microsoft%20President%20Brad%20Smith%20told%20NDTV%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20global%20business%20leaders%20met%20in%20Delhi%20ahead%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Smith%20also%20spoke%20on%20the%20potential%20dangers%20of%20AI%20and%20the%20future%20of%20generative%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%2C%20explaining%20they%20while%20they%20will%20certainly%20revolutionise%20the%20world%20they%20do%20also%20need%20a%20strong%20system%20of%20checks%20and%20balances%20to%20ensure%20AI%20%26quot%3Bremains%20under%20human%20control%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20AI%20is%20a%20tool%20that%20can%20help%20people%20think%20smarter%20and%20find%20answers%20more%20quickly%20(but)%20we%20shouldn't%20stop%20thinking.%20AI%20can%20make%20us%20more%20productive%20and%20more%20successful%2C%20it%20can%20help%20us%20translate%20from%20one%20language%20to%20another...%20I%20think%20it%20can%20be%20a%20source%20of%20more%20growth%20and%20creation%20of%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Microsoft%20boss%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20future%20of%20generative%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20-%20a%20language%20model-based%20chatbot%20developed%20by%20OpenAI%20and%20launched%20in%20November%20last%20year%20-%20Mr%20Smith%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20the%20future%20of%20what%20we%20call%20generative%20AI%20is%2C%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20just%20getting%20started.%20It%20can%20make%20doctors%20more%20effective%20at%20diagnosing%20diseases%20and%20help%20find%20new%20drugs%20to%20cure%20diseases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20used%20as%20tutors%20for%20students%20and%20for%20parents%20to%20work%20with%20their%20children...%20more%20than%20anything%20else%2C%20I%20think%20AI%20is%20will%20be%20as%20important%20to%20the%20future%20of%20knowledge%20as%20the%20printing%20press%20was%20when%20it%20was%20invented%20(nearly%20600%20years%20ago).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%2C%20also%2C%20the%20Microsoft%20leader%20stressed%2C%20is%20to%20ensure%20AI%20does%20not%20ever%20pose%20a%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20ensure%20AI%20always%20remains%20under%20human%20control%20and%20the%20best%20time%20to%20put%20in%20place%20safety%20checks%20and%20systems%20to%20guard%20(against%20dangers%20of%20AI)%20is%20now.%20We%20need%20companies%20to%20develop%20AI%20in%20a%20responsible%20manner...%20the%20focus%20must%20be%20on%20new%20laws%20and%20regulations%2C%20and%20this%20has%20to%20be%20an%20international%20effort%2C%20yes%2C%20and%20within%20each%20country%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20Mr%20Smith%2C%20said%20will%20play%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20not%20magic...%20it%20is%20not%20an%20independent%20source%20of%20knowledge%20and%20it%20not%20sentient.%20It%20is%20math.%20I%20think%20there%20may%20be%20a%20distant%20future%20when%20that%20is%20different%20but%20that%20too%20is%20a%20reason%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20'now'%20and%20ensure%20this%20technology%20serves%20humanity%20and%20remains%20under%20human%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Smith%20also%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20on%20remarkable%20strides%20taken%20by%20India%20in%20digitalisation%20at%20various%20levels%20and%20in%20various%20sectors%2C%20including%20the%20now-ubiquitous%20digital%20payments%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20is%20no%20country%2C%20that%20I%20have%20seen%2C%20that%20has%20advanced%20so%20far%20and%20so%20quickly%20(as%20India)%2C%20especially%20since%20this%20decade%20began.%20And%20from%20our%20perspective%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20what%20we%20see%20is%20not%20only%20what%20digital%20systems%20are%20doing%20for%20public%20infrastructure%20in%20India%20but%20what%20it%20can%20do%20for%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20can%20do%20even%20more%20now%20that%20we%20are%20bringing%20AI%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Microsoft%20President%20concluded%20by%20stressing%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20India%20to%20his%20company%2C%20explaining%2C%20it%20means%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20amount%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20remains%20a%20source%20of%20top%20engineering%20talent%2C%20great%20innovations%20and%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692956760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F2pvqu768_microsoft-president-brad-smith-1200_625x300_25_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fb20-summit-delhi-microsoft-president-brad-smith-to-ndtv-ai-can-be-source-of-jobs-must-be-in-human-control-microsofts-boss-to-ndtv-4328640%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Art