20Tamilisai%20Soundararajan%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%20was%20delivered%20on%20August%2016.%20Details%20of%20the%20judgement%20were%20reported%20on%20today%20by%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fmadras-high-court%2Fmadras-high-court-lois-sophia-raising-fascist-bjp-down-slogan-not-an-offence-236167%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20significantly%20held%20that%20raising%20a%20slogan%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfascist%20BJP%2C%20down%E2%80%9D%20is%20not%20an%20offence%20and%20called%20it%20a%20trivial%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20research%20scholar%20Lois%20Sofia%2C%20had%20raised%20the%20slogan%20at%20the%20Thoothukudi%20airport%20and%20in%20the%20flight%20which%20had%20Soundararajan%2C%20who%20is%20now%20governor%20of%20Telangana%20and%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20of%20Puducherry.%20Videos%20had%20show%20Tamilisai%20Soundararajan%20shouting%20at%20Sofia%20when%20she%20raised%20the%20slogans%20at%20the%20airport.%20Sofia%20was%20arrested%20afterwards%20and%20was%20granted%20bail%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fmadras-high-court-quashes-fir-against-research-scholar-lois-sofia-for-shouting-anti-bjp-slogans-2650353%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHerald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Sofia%20in%202019%20through%20which%20he%20sought%20the%20quashing%20of%20the%20FIR%20filed%20against%20her%20by%20Thoothukudi%20police%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESofia%20was%20booked%20under%20sections%20290%20(punishment%20for%20public%20nuisance%20in%20cases%20not%20otherwise%20provided%20for)%20and%2075%20(1)%20(C)%20of%20the%20Madras%20City%20Police%20Act%2C%20%3Cem%3EDH%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20The%20latter%20pertains%20to%C2%A0penalty%20for%20drunkenness%20or%20riotous%20or%20indecent%20behaviour%20in%20public%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20sections%20are%20both%20non-cognisable%20offences.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20court%20pointed%20out%20on%20August%2016%2C%20a%20Section%20505(1)(b)%20of%20the%20IPC%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20a%20cognisable%20offence%20and%20can%20thus%20alter%20the%20case%20into%20a%20cognisable%20one%20%E2%80%93%20was%20later%20hand-written%20into%20the%20printed%20FIR%20even%20though%20there%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20non%20cognisable%20offences%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20present%20BJP%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20case%20intervenor%20K.%20Annamalai%20said%20that%20police%20had%20failed%20to%20register%20a%20case%20under%20the%20Suppression%20of%20Unlawful%20Acts%20against%20Safety%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20Act%201982%2C%20the%20court%20said%20turned%20down%20the%20possibility%20citing%20the%20fact%20that%C2%A0mere%20uttering%20of%20a%20word%20is%20not%20likely%20to%20endanger%20the%20safety%20of%20an%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20P%20Dhanabal%20of%20the%20Madurai%20bench%20further%20said%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20Sofia%E2%80%99s%20actions%20which%20can%20warrant%20the%20invocation%20of%20public%20nuisance%20under%20section%20290%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20which%20pertains%20to%20public%20nuisance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20First%20Information%20Report%20and%20the%20charge%20sheet%20discloses%20that%20the%20petitioner%20only%20raised%20slogan%20as%20%E2%80%98Fascist%20B.J.P%E2%80%99%20and%20those%20words%20do%20not%20constitute%20any%20offence%20and%20it%20is%20trivial%20in%20nature%C2%A0%20Therefore%20as%20discussed%20supra%2C%20the%20charge%20sheet%20in%20S.T.C.No.%20324%20of%202018%20on%20the%20file%20of%20the%20learned%20Judicial%20Magistrate%20No.III%2C%20Thoothukudi%20is%20liable%20to%20be%20quashed%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20order%20says%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20that%20due%20procedure%20under%20Section%20155%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%20was%20not%20followed%20by%20police%20after%20the%20plea%20for%20her%20remand%20under%20Section%20505%20was%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692955995000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25150140%2Fmdu2a.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flois-sofia-tamilisai-soundararajan-fascist-bjp-down%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202018%2C%20research%20scholar%20Lois%20Sofia%20had%20raised%20the%20slogan%20at%20the%20Thoothukudi%20airport%20and%20in%20a%20flight%20which%20had%20Tamilisai%20Soundararajan%2C%20who%20is%20now%20governor%20of%20Telangana%20and%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20of%20Puducherry%2C%20and%20was%20then%20TN%20BJP%20chief.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flois-sofia-tamilisai-soundararajan-fascist-bjp-down%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%20Does%20What%20He%20Can%20To%20Salvage%20Dream%20Girl%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20laughably%20vacuous%20script%20isn't%20the%20only%20undoing%20of%20%3Cem%3EDream%20Girl%202%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20comedy%20caper%20opens%20with%20a%20jagrata%20sequence%20capped%20by%20a%20song%20and%20dance%20performed%20by%20lead%20actor%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana.%20Taking%20a%20cue%20from%20him%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cast%20treats%20the%20film%20like%20an%20all-nighter%20without%20a%20morrow%20and%20ham%20their%20way%20through%20an%20utterly%20unfunny%20concoction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirected%20by%20Raaj%20Shaandilyaa%2C%20who%20helmed%20the%202019%20precursor%2C%20%3Cem%3EDream%20Girl%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20the%20likes%20of%20Vijay%20Raaz%20and%20Seema%20Pahwa%2C%20actors%20who%20are%20usually%20totally%20reliable%2C%20but%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20is%20left%20entirely%20to%20Khurrana.%20He%20does%20what%20he%20can%20to%20salvage%20a%20stale%20storyline%20that%20is%20as%20hollow%20as%20a%20drum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20until%20a%20pre-climactic%20sequence%2C%20which%20allows%20Khurrana's%20character%20to%20launch%20into%20a%20self-righteous%20tirade%20against%20everyone%20within%20earshot%2C%20that%20the%20actor%20comes%20into%20his%20own.%20The%20series%20of%20supposedly%20comic%20scenes%20that%20precede%20it%20is%2C%20however%2C%20a%20totally%20wasted%20tickle%20fight%20-%20it%20does%20not%20yield%20the%20expected%20laugh%20riot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20stray%20scene%2C%20the%20hero%20who%20spends%20most%20of%20the%20film%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20married%20woman%20he%20says%20to%20a%20character%20enamoured%20with%20'her'%3A%20aise%20mat%20ro%2C%20mujhe%20hansi%20aa%20jayegi%20(don't%20cry%2C%20I'll%20break%20into%20laughter).%20The%20comedy%20has%20the%20reverse%20effect%3A%20it%20reduces%20the%20audience%20either%20to%20tears%20or%20lulls%20them%20into%20the%20sort%20of%20impassivity%20that%20lasts%20the%20entire%20duration%20of%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMathura%20resident%20Karam%20Singh%20(Khurrana)%2C%20a%20jobless%20gender-shifting%20jagrata%20performer%2C%20is%20in%20love%20with%20budding%20lawyer%20Pari%20Shrivastava%20(Ananya%20Panday).%20But%20since%20his%20father%2C%20Jagjeet%20Singh%20(Annu%20Kapoor)%2C%20is%20buried%20under%20a%20mountain%20of%20debt%20and%20their%20ancestral%20home%20is%20a%20crumbling%20mess%2C%20the%20girl's%20dad%20(Manoj%20Joshi)%20lays%20down%20conditions%20for%20the%20suitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFind%20a%20job%2C%20renovate%20your%20home%20and%20build%20up%20a%20substantial%20bank%20balance%20and%20only%20then%20ask%20for%20my%20daughter's%20hand%2C%20the%20money-minded%20patriarch%20says.%20Karam%2C%20egged%20on%20by%20his%20best%20pal%20Smiley%20(Manjot%20Singh)%2C%20takes%20a%20shot%20at%20being%20a%20bar%20dancer%20at%20a%20nightclub%20owned%20by%20Saajan%20%26quot%3BSona%20Bhai%26quot%3B%20Tiwari%20(Vijay%20Raaz).%20The%20money%20is%20good%20but%20is%20it%20good%20enough%3F%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmiley%20loves%20Sakina%20(Anusha%20Mishra).%20It%20is%20now%20this%20girl's%20dad%20Abu%20Saleem's%20(Paresh%20Rawal)%20turn%20to%20put%20his%20foot%20down%20and%20make%20a%20demand%20of%20his%20own.%20Get%20my%20son%2C%20Mohammed%20Shahrukh%20(Abhishek%20Banerjee)%2C%20out%20of%20the%20deep%20funk%20that%20he%20has%20sunk%20into%20since%20his%20break-up%20with%20his%20girlfriend%2C%20he%20says%20to%20the%20ever-jovial%20Smiley%2C%20before%20you%20wed%20Sakina.%20Karam%2C%20impersonating%20Pooja%2C%20re-enters%20the%20scene%20pretending%20to%20be%20a%20shrink%20to%20help%20his%20friend%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FdlC1tNsr-n8%3Fsi%3DLmlE_BLb0ohQ2QIJ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comedy%20of%20errors%20and%20messy%20cross-connections%20between%20members%20of%20Abu%20Saleem's%20messed-up%20family%20and%20Karam's%20cash-strapped%20dad%20and%20supportive%20friend%20is%20marred%20by%20the%20writing%20(by%20the%20director%20and%20Naresh%20Kathooria).%20It%20never%20rises%20above%20the%20pedestrian.%20One%20does%20laugh%20at%20what%20is%20going%20on%20but%20for%20all%20the%20wrong%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20jokes%20that%20the%20characters%20crack%20ride%20on%20Sunny%20Deol%2F%3Cem%3EGadar%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Shahrukh%20Khan%2F%3Cem%3EPathaan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20fall%20flat.%20But%20they%20are%20inoffensive%2C%20if%20not%20passable%2C%20but%20what%20isn't%20acceptable%20at%20all%20is%20that%20%3Cem%3EDream%20Girl%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20pokes%20fun%20at%20sexual%20orientation%2C%20gender%20fluidity%2C%20adoption%20and%20even%20depression%20(and%20the%20psychiatrist's%20profession)%20in%20its%20quest%20for%20lowbrow%20comicality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20hero%20of%20%3Cem%3EDream%20Girl%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20masquerades%20as%20a%20woman%20so%20that%20he%20can%20make%20the%20money%20he%20needs%20to%20marry%20the%20girl%20he%20loves%2C%20the%20film%20has%20only%20two%20women.%20One%20is%20the%20hero's%20girlfriend%20who%20breathes%20hot%20and%20cold%20as%20the%20male%20protagonist%20switches%20genders%20at%20the%20snap%20of%20a%20finger%2C%20frequently%20inviting%20trouble%20in%20the%20process.%20The%20other%20is%20a%20much-married%20older%20woman%2C%20Jumani%20(Seema%20Pahwa)%2C%20who%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20messy%20divorce%20and%20desperately%20seeking%20a%20fourth%20hubby%20if%20that%20means%20jumping%20into%20a%20bigger%20muddle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20other%20women%20who%20should%20logically%20have%20been%20around%20or%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20been%20accounted%20for%20are%20non-existent.%20Karam's%20father%20is%20a%20widower%20and%20so%20is%20Sakina's%20dad.%20And%20there%20is%20nary%20a%20mention%20of%20Pari's%20mother.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20presume%20that%20her%20dad%2C%20too%2C%20does%20not%20have%20a%20wife%20anymore.%20Wonder%20what%20the%20logic%20might%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audience%20might%20want%20look%20for%20a%20clue%20in%20a%20line%20that%20Karam%2FPooja%20delivers%20in%20order%20to%20enlighten%20a%20bemused%20Smiley%3A%20Tujhe%20pata%20nahi%20kitna%20mushkil%20hota%20hai%20ladki%20banna%20(You%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20become%20a%20woman).%20He%20does%20not%20stop%20there.%20He%20ends%20the%20thought%20with%20Ussey%20bhi%20mushkil%20hota%20hota%20hai%20ladki%20hona%20(It%20is%20even%20mor%20difficult%20to%20be%20a%20woman).%20That%20is%20all%20the%20wokeness%20that%20%3Cem%3EDream%20Girl%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20can%20muster.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20far%20the%20funniest%20of%20the%20characters%20in%20this%20uninspired%20comedy%20is%20a%20bank%20employee%20named%20Tiger%20Pandey%20(Ranjan%20Raj)%2C%20who%20falls%20in%20love%20with%20Pooja's%20voice%20on%20the%20phone%20(a%20la%20the%20lovers%20he%2Fshe%20had%20in%202019's%20%3Cem%3EDream%20Girl%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20looks%20for%20her%20all%20across%20Agra%20and%20Mathura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Unfortunately%2C%20he%20is%20the%20most%20dispensable%20of%20all%20the%20men%20hovering%20over%20Pooja.%20He%20appears%20only%20to%20be%20ridiculed%20left%20and%20right%20and%20then%20disappears%20only%20to%20reappear%20and%20be%20treated%20like%20a%20punching%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hero%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%20Dream%20Girl%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20to%20make%20frequent%20visits%20to%20the%20toilet%20to%20get%20his%20oranges%20in%20place%20as%20he%20repeatedly%20transitions%20between%20genders.%20If%20only%20the%20makers%2C%20out%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20the%20success%20of%202019's%20%3Cem%3EDream%20Girl%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20knew%20their%20onions%20better%2C%20the%20meagre%20amount%20of%20juice%20that%20they%20extract%20from%20an%20idea%20that%20has%20been%20wrung%20thin%20would%20have%20been%20tangier%2C%20if%20nothing%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20credit%20of%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%2C%20he%20never%20gives%20the%20impression%20that%20he%20is%20on%20a%20sinking%20ship.%20He%20does%20not%20hold%20back%20one%20bit%20even%20when%20the%20writing%20lets%20him%20down.%20Manjot%20Singh%2C%20when%20the%20script%20permits%2C%20soldiers%20on%20gamely%20and%20lends%20the%20lead%20actor%20some%20support.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20an%20array%20of%20seasoned%20actors%20with%20enviable%20track%20records%20are%20reduced%20to%20merely%20going%20through%20the%20motions%2C%20you%20know%20you%20are%20watching%20a%20film%20that%20does%20not%20know%20where%20it%20is%20headed.%20We%20the%20audience%20figure%20out%20pretty%20quickly%3A%20this%20one%20is%20going%20nowhere.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692955860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F9ubf75m8_aayush_625x300_25_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdream-girl-2-review-ayushmann-khurrana-does-what-he-can-to-salvage-a-stale-storyline-1-5-stars-4328650%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dream%20Girl%202%20Review%3A%20To%20the%20credit%20of%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%2C%20he%20never%20gives%20the%20impression%20that%20he%20is%20on%20a%20sinking%20ship.%20He%20does%20not%20hold%20back%20one%20bit%20even%20when%20the%20writing%20lets%20him%20down.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdream-girl-2-review-ayushmann-khurrana-does-what-he-can-to-salvage-a-stale-storyline-1-5-stars-4328650%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdream-girl-2-review-ayushmann-khurrana-does-what-he-can-to-salvage-a-stale-storyline-1-5-stars-4328650%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdream-girl-2-review-ayushmann-khurrana-does-what-he-can-to-salvage-a-stale-storyline-1-5-stars-4328650%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20Those%20Demanding%20a%20New%20Constitution%20Are%20Fighting%20for%20a%20Less%20Equal%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F20153953%2FIMG_4436.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EDr%20Bibek%20Debroy%20is%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20economic%20advisory%20council%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20obviously%20very%20close%20to%20the%20centres%20of%20power%20in%20more%20sense%20than%20one.%20He%20recently%20(August%2015)%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fopinion%2Fonline-views%2Ftheres-a-case-for-we-the-people-to-embrace-a-new-constitution-11692021963182.html%5C%22%3Earticle%20in%20%3Cem%3ELivemint%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20questioned%20the%20continuation%20of%20the%20present%20Constitution.%20For%20him%20this%20is%20not%20the%20same%20Constitution%20which%20was%20adopted%20after%20Independence%20as%20it%20has%20been%20amended%20many%20times.%20As%20per%20him%2C%20since%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20ruled%20that%20the%20executive%20cannot%20change%20its%20basic%20structure%20and%20it%20has%20outlived%20its%20time%2C%20we%20should%20prepare%20for%20a%20new%20constitution.%20More%20importantly%20he%20says%20this%20Constitution%20is%20a%20colonial%20legacy%20and%20questions%20various%20provisions%20of%20the%20same%2C%20particularly%20the%20values%20of%20socialism%2C%20secularism%2C%20justice%2C%20equality%20and%20liberty.%20The%20advisory%20council%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbibek-debroy-article-for-new-constitution-pm-panel-says-not-our-view-8897462%2F%5C%22%3Eofficially%20distanced%20itself%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20opinions%20expressed%20by%20Debroy%20but%20the%20purpose%20of%20raising%20doubts%20and%20opposition%20to%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20has%20been%20raised%20successfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%20the%20ideologues%20and%20leaders%20from%20the%20Hindu%20right%20have%20been%20asserting%20that%20this%20constitution%20is%20a%20colonial%20legacy%2C%20based%20on%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20Act%20of%201935%20of%20the%20British%20and%20does%20not%20reflect%20%E2%80%98Indian%20values%E2%80%99.%20Right-wing%20Hindu%20nationalists%20were%20never%20comfortable%20with%20this%20Constitution%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20mere%20continuation%20of%20the%20GOI%20act%20of%201935%2C%20but%20prepared%20after%20painstaking%20debates%20for%20nearly%20three%20years%20and%20meticulously%20put%20forward%20by%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20drafting%20committee%20of%20Indian%20Constitution%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar.%20The%20president%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20Dr%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20and%20most%20members%20were%20the%20ones%20who%20identified%20with%20the%20anti-colonial%20struggle%20of%20Indian%20people.%20It%20was%20this%20struggle%20which%20also%20was%20crucial%20in%20the%20formation%20of%20%E2%80%98India%20as%20a%20Nation%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20those%20who%20stood%20for%20plural%2C%20inclusive%20Indian%20nationalism%2C%20the%20religious%20nationalists%20stood%20away%20from%20this%20great%20struggle%20and%20also%20opposed%20the%20values%20which%20emerged%20with%20this%20mass%20movement.%20As%20the%20Constitution%20was%20implemented%2C%20the%20RSS%20mouthpiece%20rejected%20it%20and%20demanded%20the%20Manusmriti%20as%20the%20Constitution.%20An%20editorial%20in%20Organiser%20on%20Novemner%2030%2C%201949%20read%3A%20%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20our%20Constitution%2C%20there%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20unique%20Constitutional%20development%20in%20Ancient%20Bharat.%20Manu%E2%80%99s%20laws%20were%20written%20long%20before%20Lycurgus%20of%20Sparata%20or%20Solon%20of%20Persia.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.academia.edu%2F35261924%2F68_TH_ANNIVERSARY_OF_INDIAN_CONSTITUTION_WHEN_NATION_CELEBRATED_ITS_ADOPTION_RSS_MOURNED_IT%5C%22%3ETo%20this%20%3C%2Fa%3Eday%20his%20laws%20as%20enunciated%20in%20the%20Manusmriti%20excite%20the%20admiration%20of%20the%20World%20and%20elicit%20spontaneous%20obedience%20and%20conformity.%20But%20to%20our%20Constitution%20pundits%20that%20means%20nothing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Safeguarding%20Academic%20Freedom%20Is%20the%20Bedrock%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Constitutional%20Morality%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsafeguarding-academic-freedom-is-the-bedrock-of-indias-constitutional-morality%5C%22%3ESafeguarding%20Academic%20Freedom%20Is%20the%20Bedrock%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Constitutional%20Morality%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20to%20the%20Constitution%20started%20being%20articulated%20more%20sternly%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Hindu%20right.%20As%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%E2%80%99s%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%201998%2C%20it%20appointed%20the%20Venkatchaliah%20Commission%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbyjus.com%2Fquestion-answer%2Fq-who-was-the-chairman-of-the-national-commission-to-review-the-working-of-the%2F%5C%22%3Ereviewing%20the%3C%2Fa%3E%20Constitution.%20The%20strong%20opposition%20to%20the%20commission%20was%20to%20the%20detriment%20to%20the%20BJP-led%20coalition%20to%20implement%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20opposition%20to%20the%20Constitution%20keeps%20manifesting%20itself%20in%20diverse%20ways.%20When%20K.%20Sudarshan%20became%20the%20%3Cem%3Esarsanghachalak%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20he%20openly%20declared%20that%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20is%20based%20on%20Western%20values%20and%20should%20be%20replaced%20by%20one%20based%20on%20Indian%20holy%20books%2C%20indicating%20the%20Manusmriti.%20He%20asserted%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20not%20fight%20shy%20of%20altering%20the%20constitution%20completely%2C%20having%20already%20amended%20it%20a%20hundred%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20said%20that%20France%20had%20done%20the%20revision%20four%20times.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20nothing%20sacrosanct%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwocircles.net%2F2007jun08%2Fconstitution-root-cause-countrys-ills-rss-chief.html%5C%22%3Eabout%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20most%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20ills.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETimes%20and%20time%20again%2C%20one%20or%20the%20other%20worthy%20from%20the%20BJP-RSS%20stable%20do%20make%20statements%20of%20this%20type.%20Recently%2C%20as%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20formed%20INDIA%2C%20many%20from%20the%20right%20came%20to%20oppose%20it%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20the%20word%20was%20coined%20by%20the%20British.%20One%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20Naresh%20Bansal%2C%20questioned%20the%20place%20of%20very%20word%20India%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fzeenews.india.com%2Findia%2Fsymbol-of-british-slavery-bjp-mp-naresh-bansal-demands-word-india-to-be-removed-from-consitution-watch-2641541.html%5C%22%3Eas%20it%20is%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20symbol%20of%20slavery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20related%20to%20their%20concept%20of%20decolonisation%20of%20minds%20as%20put%20forward%20by%20RSS%20general%20secretary%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Euro-centric%20ideas%2C%20systems%20and%20practices%2C%20the%20western%20world%20view%20were%20still%20ruling%20us%20for%20decades.%20Independent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Findias-educated-class-continues-to-remain-in-mental-slavery-rss-leader-dattatreya-hosabale%2Farticle66477413.ece%5C%22%3Enation%20didn%E2%80%99t%3C%2Fa%3E%20shirk%20them%20totally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebroy%20and%20the%20RSS%20stable%20merged%20on%20the%20point%20of%20opposition%20to%20the%20Constitution.%20While%20the%20RSS%20combine%20focuses%20more%20on%20its%20Western%20nature%2C%20Debroy%20lets%20the%20cat%20out%20of%20the%20bag%20when%20he%20questions%20the%20values%20of%20liberty%2C%20equality%2C%20secularism%20and%20the%20like.%20The%20colonial%20legacy%20argument%20is%20akin%20to%20the%20organisations%20like%20that%20of%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20Brotherhood%E2%80%99%20of%20West%20Asian%20countries%2C%20which%20oppose%20the%20values%20of%20liberty%20and%20equality%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20they%20are%20Western.%20Debroy%20and%20apologists%20of%20the%20present%20regime%20are%20disturbed%20by%20the%20concept%20of%20equality%20%E2%80%93%20equality%20between%20people%20of%20different%20religions%2C%20castes%20and%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Constitution%20and%20the%20Wrath%20of%20(We)%20the%20People%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-constitution-and-the-wrath-of-we-the-people%5C%22%3EThe%20Constitution%20and%20the%20Wrath%20of%20(We)%20the%20People%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20combine%20projects%20the%20era%20of%20the%20Manusmriti%20as%20a%20Golden%20Past%2C%20as%20caste%20and%20gender%20hierarchies%20were%20the%20core%20of%20the%20society%20at%20the%20time.%20It%20is%20during%20the%20colonial%20period%20that%20caste%20and%20gender%20hierarchies%20started%20loosening%20their%20grip%2C%20it%20is%20during%20this%20period%20that%20workers%20could%20make%20their%20organisations%20(Narayan%20Meghaji%20Lokhande%2C%20Com%20Singarvelu)%2C%20it%20is%20during%20this%20period%20the%20likes%20of%20Bhagat%20Singh%20articulated%20the%20exploitation%20by%20the%20ruling%20classes%2C%20which%20needed%20to%20be%20done%20away%20with.%20Much%20of%20this%20was%20spearheaded%20by%20Indians%2C%20while%20under%20colonial%20rule%20and%20also%20struggling%20against%20colonial%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20colonial%20period%20cannot%20be%20looked%20at%20as%20black%20or%20white.%20It%20has%20shades%20of%20grey.%20While%20colonial%20powers%20plundered%20our%20wealth%2C%20they%20also%20had%20to%20open%20up%20institutions%20which%20were%20to%20articulate%20the%20%E2%80%9CEquality%20of%20Man%20(and%20Women)%E2%80%9D.%20The%20RSS%20combine%20and%20the%20advisor%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20may%20be%20giving%20different%20arguments%20for%20doing%20away%20with%20this%20constitution%2C%20but%20in%20essence%20they%20are%20opposed%20to%20equality%2C%20which%20was%20the%20hallmark%20of%20the%20values%20propounded%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20the%20struggles%20launched%20by%20Ambedkar%20and%20the%20overarching%20national%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20the%201990s%2C%20the%20country%20did%20try%20to%20pursue%20the%20path%20of%20equality%2C%20with%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20as%20the%20fulcrum%20and%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20modernisation%20policies.%20Now%20we%20seem%20to%20be%20moving%20in%20the%20reverse%20gear.%20With%20the%20temple%20and%20the%20cow%20dominating%20the%20scene%2C%20the%20path%20towards%20inequality%20is%20being%20carved%20by%20invoking%20ancient%20values%2C%20a%20Brahamanical%20interpretation%20of%20the%20past%20(labelled%20as%20%E2%80%98civilisational%20values%E2%80%99)%20and%20undermining%20what%20we%20achieved%20through%20the%20greatest%20ever%20mass%20movement%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20Indian%20freedom%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20opposition%20to%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20is%20a%20mere%20reuse%20to%20push%20the%20country%20back%20to%20the%20era%20where%20inequality%20(of%20caste%2C%20class%20and%20gender)%20was%20sanctified%20by%20religion%20(Brahmanism).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fram-puniyani%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERam%20Puniyani%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20president%2C%20Centre%20of%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism%20and%20has%20written%20several%20books%20including%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3ECommunal%20Politics%3A%20Facts%20Versus%20Myths%3Cem%3E%C2%A0(Sage%2C%202003)%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EDeconstructing%20Terrorist%20Violence%3Cem%3E%C2%A0(Sage%202015)%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EIndian%20Nationalism%20versus%20Hindu%20Nationalism%3Cem%3E%C2%A0(Pharos%202014)%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eand%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3ECaste%20and%20Communalism%3Cem%3E%C2%A0(Olive%202013).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692955859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F20153953%2FIMG_4436.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fall-those-demanding-a-new-constitution-are-fighting-for-a-less-equal-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20recent%20article%2C%20Bibek%20Debroy%20highlighted%20the%20Hindu%20right's%20real%20problem%20with%20the%20Constitution%3A%20values%20of%20unity%2C%20equality%2C%20secularism%20and%20so%20on.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fall-those-demanding-a-new-constitution-are-fighting-for-a-less-equal-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUr