20rentals.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETheir%20treehouse%20rental%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20listings%20on%20Airbnb%20for%20unique%20spaces.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20are%20now%20expanding%20their%20business%20internationally%20in%20countires%20like%20Belize.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Patrice%20Maxam%20and%20Darrel%20Maxam%20in%20Atlanta%20Georgia%2C%20who%20own%20unique%20Airbnb%20properties.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhen%20we%20first%20started%20our%20Airbnb%20business%20in%202015%2C%20we%20began%20by%20renting%20out%20bungalows%20and%20smaller%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBut%20after%20doing%20some%20research%2C%20and%20after%20staying%20in%20many%20Airbnbs%20ourselves%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20build%20our%20first%20treehouse%20rental.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20noticed%20treehouse%20Airbnbs%20were%20popular%20and%20they%20are%20timeless%2C%20too.%20They're%20unique%20and%20seem%20to%20command%20a%20higher%20price%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESo%2C%20we%20thought%20if%20we%20were%20going%20to%20have%20an%20Airbnb%20business%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20do%20something%20a%20bit%20more%20unique%20and%20different.%20Since%20then%2C%20raised%20structures%20or%20Airbnbs%20that%20aren't%20on%20the%20ground%20have%20become%20our%20niche.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOverall%20we%20have%20seven%20Airbnb%20properties%20located%20in%20New%20York%20and%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20and%20three%20of%20them%20are%20treehouses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERenovating%20a%20Airbnb%20treehouse%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202021%2C%20we%20put%20up%20what%20became%20our%20most%20popular%20treehouse%2C%20called%20Young%20Wild%20and%20Tree.%20It's%20a%20converted%201956%20Spartan%20trailer%20with%20a%201957%20retro%20vibe%20for%20the%20interior.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22561%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Weave%20basket%20ceiling.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e7a7d1a7adf7001907629c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22421%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20weave%20basket%20ceiling%20in%20the%20Young%20Wild%20and%20Tree%20treehouse.%3Cp%3EPatrice%20Maxam%20and%20Darrel%20Maxam%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhen%20renovating%2C%20one%20thing%20we%20had%20to%20tackle%20was%20the%20ceiling.%20It%20was%20Darrel%20who%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20styling%20the%20ceiling%20like%20a%20weave%20basket.%20Darrel%20and%20his%20assistant%20did%20that%2C%20the%20entire%20thing%20took%20them%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20weeks%20to%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22554%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sticker%20wall%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e7a852a7adf70019076359%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22415%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sticker%20wall%20in%20Young%20Wild%20and%20Tree%3Cp%3EPatrice%20Maxam%20and%20Darrel%20Maxam%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAnother%20cool%20feature%20is%20the%20sticker%20wall%2C%20when%20we%20purchased%20the%20trailer%20it%20came%20with%20a%20broken%20window.%20So%20I%20thought%2C%20let's%20go%20with%20the%20vibe%20of%20broken%20glass.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThen%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20decorate%20it%20with%20Atlanta%20themed%20stickers.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20searched%20for%20stickers%20that%20represented%20LGBTQ%2C%20Black%20Lives%20Matter%2C%20and%20hip%20hop%20music%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEverytime%20a%20new%20sticker%20came%20in%20the%20mail%2C%20it%20would%20arrive%20in%20a%20brown%20envelope.%20We%20probably%20got%20close%20to%2050%20brown%20envelopes%2C%20and%20our%20kids%20would%20get%20excited%20each%20time.%20It%20felt%20like%20Christmas%20whenever%20we%20got%20to%20place%20a%20new%20sticker%20onto%20the%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAt%20first%2C%20we%20were%20simply%20trying%20to%20hide%20an%20imperfection%20and%20it%20ended%20up%20becoming%20a%20huge%20statement%20piece.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20challenges%20of%20an%20Airbnb%20treehouse%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWith%20every%20new%20Airbnb%20project%20there%20will%20always%20be%20hiccups%20and%20challenges.%20For%20example%2C%20sometimes%2C%20things%20take%20longer%20than%20planned%2C%20there%20are%20extra%20labor%20costs%2C%20or%20there%20is%20something%20new%20to%20figure%20out.%20We're%20always%20learning%20how%20to%20address%20those%20hiccups%20when%20they%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22549%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Batroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e7af05a7adf70019076a3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22412%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20private%20bathroom%20space.%3Cp%3EPatrice%20Maxam%20and%20Darrel%20Maxam%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20bathroom%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20brain%20power%20due%20to%20the%20plumbing.%20We%20wondered%20how%20we%20would%20run%20water%20into%20our%20treehouse.%20Eventually%20we%20decided%20to%20put%20the%20bathroom%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20a%20lower%20structure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20also%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20build%20a%20staircase%20around%20a%20tree%2C%20or%20a%20curved%20object%20that%20would%20change%20in%20shape%20and%20size.%20We%20had%20to%20wrap%20our%20minds%20around%20the%20circumference%20and%20the%20radius%20of%20the%20tree%20and%20tap%20back%20into%20high%20school%20geometry%20class.%20It%20was%20tough%20but%20eventually%20we%20figured%20it%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20stand%20out%20on%20Airbnb%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIf%20you're%20interested%20in%20having%20an%20Airbnb%20of%20your%20own%2C%20we%20learned%20you%20should%20make%20it%20unique.%20Try%20to%20think%2C%20what%20will%20guests%20be%20excited%20about%3F%20Or%20why%20is%20your%20Airbnb%20different%20from%20the%20other%20Airbnbs%20on%20the%20market%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20our%20experience%2C%20guests%20also%20like%20it%20when%20you%20make%20the%20space%20feel%20homey%2C%20and%20personable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EYou%20can%20do%20that%20by%20offering%20personalized%20things%20for%20your%20guests%20when%20they%20arrive.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20once%20realized%20it%20was%20our%20guests%2073rd%20birthday%2C%20so%20to%20celebrate%20we%20asked%20for%20his%20favorite%20type%20of%20wine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThen%20when%20he%20arrived%20in%20his%20unit%2C%20we%20made%20sure%20the%20wine%20was%20chilled.%20We%20also%20gave%20him%20a%20bouquet%20of%20flowers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20would%20like%20to%20have%20an%20Airbnb%2C%20realize%20it's%20the%20little%20details%20that%20matter%20and%20try%20to%20make%20your%20guests%20smile%20when%20they%20enter%20your%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFuture%20Airbnb%20projects%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBack%20in%202020%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20purchased%20land%20in%20Belize%20and%20are%20planning%20on%20building%20an%20Airbnb%20there.%20The%20property%20is%20about%20an%20eighth%20of%20a%20mile%20away%20from%20the%20beach%20and%20has%20a%20good%20view%20of%20the%20ocean%20and%20the%20sunset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20also%20have%20other%20places%20that%20we're%20dreaming%20of%20starting%20Airbnbs%20in%2C%20like%20Africa.%20We%20have%20really%20big%20international%20dreams%20and%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20growing%20our%20unique