ated%20the%20successful%20landing%20of%20Chandrayaan-3's%20lunar%20module%20on%20the%20moon's%20surface%20on%20Wednesday.%20Former%20India%20captain%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni%20was%20one%20of%20the%20several%20excited%20citizens%20who%20waited%20to%20witness%20this%20historic%20moment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fwatch-ms-dhoni-celebrates-the-successful-landing-of-chandrayaan-3%2Farticleshow%2F103056053.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20Set%20to%20Change%20How%20News%20Links%20Appear%20on%20X%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F02102823%2F46339127625_054ddd1a61_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20is%20set%20to%20change%20how%20news%20links%20appear%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20despite%20opposition%20from%20advertisers%2C%20%3Cem%3EFortune%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F08%2F21%2Felon-musk-plans-remove-headlines-news-articles-link-shared-on-x-twitter%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20links%20will%20now%20appear%20without%20a%20headline%20and%20any%20other%20text%20with%20only%20the%20article%E2%80%99s%20lead%20image%20on%20display%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20reportedly%20spearheaded%20by%20Elon%20Musk%20himself%20who%20confirmed%20the%20upcoming%20change%20in%20a%20tweet.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20coming%20from%20me%20directly.%20Will%20greatly%20improve%20the%20esthetics%20(sic)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20coming%20from%20me%20directly.%20Will%20greatly%20improve%20the%20esthetics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1693843680904216619%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20means%20that%20anyone%20sharing%20a%20link%20on%20the%20platform%20would%20need%20to%20manually%20add%20their%20own%20text%20alongside%20the%20links%20they%20share%20on%20the%20platform%3B%20otherwise%20the%20tweet%20will%20display%20only%20an%20image%20with%20no%20context%20other%20than%20an%20overlay%20of%20the%20URL%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EFortune%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20clicking%20on%20the%20image%20will%20still%20lead%20the%20user%20to%20the%20article%20or%20website%20but%20the%20move%20is%20bound%20to%20affect%20advertisers%20as%20well%20as%20publishers%20who%20rely%20on%20social%20media%20to%20drive%20traffic%20to%20their%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20something%20Elon%20wants.%20They%20were%20running%20it%20by%20advertisers%2C%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20it%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20happening%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20source%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20Fortune%2C%20adding%20that%20Musk%20thinks%20articles%20occupy%20excessive%20space%20on%20the%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20links%20on%20the%20platform%20are%20currently%20accompanied%20by%20several%20elements%3A%20an%20image%2C%20a%20short%20headline%2C%20and%20a%20brief%20description%20of%20the%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EGuardian%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2Faug%2F22%2Felon-musk-x-twitter-changes-news-links%5C%22%3Emove%20may%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20drive%20people%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20X%E2%80%99s%20premium%20service%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20the%20shortened%20links%2C%20users%20could%20be%20inclined%20to%20include%20more%20text%20along%20with%20their%20posts.%20The%20premium%20service%20allows%20a%20single%20post%20of%20up%20to%2025%2C000%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20call%20for%20longer%20posts%20contradicts%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20reduce%20the%20amount%20of%20space%20tweets%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tech-mogul%20has%20made%20a%20series%20of%20arbitrary%20changes%20since%20he%20bought%20the%20platform%20in%20October%202022%20including%20banning%20journalists%20from%20the%20platform%2C%20increasing%20the%20character%20limit%2C%20paid%20verification%20badges%20and%20reinstating%20banned%20users%20like%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692954912000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F02102823%2F46339127625_054ddd1a61_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Felon-musk-set-to-change-how-news-links-appear-on-x%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20links%20will%20now%20appear%20without%20a%20headline%20and%20any%20other%20text%20with%20only%20the%20article%E2%80%99s%20lead%20image%20on%20display.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Felon-musk-set-to-change-how-news-links-appear-on-x%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengal%20Vande%20Bharat%20Coaches%20Replaced%20After%20Tech%20Glitch%2C%20Passengers%20Protest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20technical%20glitch%20in%20the%20rake%20of%20the%20Howrah-New%20Jalpaiguri%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20on%20Friday%20morning%20forced%20the%20railways%20to%20replace%20it%20with%20the%20one%20used%20in%20operating%20Yuva%20Express%2C%20causing%20a%20delay%20of%20one%20hour%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20passengers%20also%20protested%20the%20change%2C%20which%20dashed%20their%20hopes%20of%20travelling%20in%20the%20swanky%20Vande%20Bharat%20rake%20that%20has%20modern%20amenities.%20They%20said%20the%20Yuva%20Express%20rake%20did%20not%20have%20the%20amenities%20they%20paid%20for%2C%20and%20was%20not%20up%20to%20the%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOwing%20to%20a%20glitch%20in%20the%20undergear%20of%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20rake%2C%20it%20had%20to%20be%20replaced%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20of%20the%20Eastern%20Railway%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Vande%20Bharat%20rake%20was%20not%20found%20to%20be%20fit%20for%20running%20and%20was%20replaced%20by%20a%20spare%20rake%2C%20which%20is%20used%20for%20Yuva%20Express%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20caused%20a%20delay%20in%20the%20departure%20of%20the%20train%20by%20one%20hour%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20passengers%20on%20the%20train%20was%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20who%20was%20travelling%20to%20Malda%20to%20meet%20the%20families%20of%20the%20migrant%20workers%20killed%20in%20the%20Mizoram%20rail%20bridge%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20such%20a%20technical%20snag%20is%20not%20expected%20in%20the%20premier%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20rake%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%20said%20he%20will%20speak%20to%20Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20who%20is%20scheduled%20to%20visit%20Kolkata%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20bring%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20railway%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Majumdar%2C%20the%20state%20BJP%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692954900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F7i4m7i1o_vande-bharat_625x300_09_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-vande-bharat-coaches-replaced-after-tech-glitch-passengers-protest-4328472%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20technical%20glitch%20in%20the%20rake%20of%20the%20Howrah-New%20Jalpaiguri%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20on%20Friday%20morning%20forced%20the%20railways%20to%20replace%20it%20with%20the%20one%20used%20in%20operating%20Yuva%20Express%2C%20causing%20a%20delay%20of%20one%20hour%2C%20an%20official%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-vande-bharat-coaches-replaced-after-tech-glitch-passengers-protest-4328472%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-vande-bharat-coaches-replaced-after-tech-glitch-passengers-protest-4328472%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-vande-bharat-coaches-replaced-after-tech-glitch-passengers-protest-4328472%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Two%2020-Year-Olds%20Beat%20Grim%20Market%20To%20Mint%20The%20Newest%20Unicorn%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EZepto%2C%20an%20instant%20grocery%20startup%20founded%20by%20a%20duo%20of%20Stanford%20University%20dropouts%2C%20both%2020%2C%20raised%20fresh%20funds%20at%20a%20%241.4%20billion%20valuation%2C%20creating%20a%20rare%20Indian%20unicorn%20amid%20a%20gloomy%20venture%20funding%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStepStone%20Group%2C%20Goodwater%20Capital%20and%20others%20invested%20a%20combined%20%24200%20million%20in%20the%20Mumbai-based%20company%2C%20it%20said%20Friday%20in%20a%20statement.%20Zepto%2C%20built%20with%20backing%20from%20startup%20incubator%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20said%20it's%20on%20track%20to%20turn%20profitable%20within%2015%20months%20and%20intends%20to%20go%20public%20in%20two%20to%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildhood%20friends%20Aadit%20Palicha%20and%20Kaivalya%20Vohra%20dropped%20out%20of%20Stanford's%20computer%20science%20program%20to%20return%20to%20India%20and%20build%20the%20startup%20when%20they%20were%20teenagers.%20They%20are%20now%20the%20youngest%20founders%20of%20any%20Indian%20unicorn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuick%20commerce%20is%20India's%20fastest-growing%20consumer%20internet%20category%2C%20scaling%20far%20more%20rapidly%20than%20segments%20like%20ride-hailing%20and%20food%20delivery%2C%26quot%3B%20Palicha%20said%20over%20video%20conference.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20India's%20fastest-growing%20consumer%20internet%20company%20and%20will%20be%20Ebitda-positive%20within%2015%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Series%20E%20round%20comes%20at%20a%20challenging%20time%20for%20the%20quick%20commerce%20segment%20globally%2C%20with%20startups%20like%20Gopuff%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Getir%20in%20Europe%20cutting%20jobs.%20Zepto%20itself%20faces%20stiffening%20competition%20from%20rivals%20in%20India%2C%20including%20Alphabet%20Inc.-backed%20Dunzo%2C%20Zomato%20Ltd.'s%20Blinkit%20and%20Naspers%20Ltd.-backed%20Instamart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStartup%20momentum%20is%20sputtering%20worldwide.%20Venture%20funding%20declined%20by%20about%2072%25%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20year%20compared%20with%20the%20same%20period%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Tracxn%20Technologies%20Ltd.%20No%20new%20unicorns%20were%20created%20in%20the%20country%20the%20first%20half%2C%20compared%20with%2019%20unicorns%20minted%20in%20the%20year-earlier%20period%2C%20according%20to%20Tracxn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZepto%20was%20founded%20in%20July%202021%20and%20now%20has%20more%20than%20220%20so-called%20dark%20stores%2C%20or%20neighborhood%20warehouses%2C%20across%20cities%20including%20Mumbai%2C%20Bangalore%20and%20New%20Delhi%2C%20with%20plans%20for%20expansion.%20Its%20early%20backers%20include%20Nexus%20Venture%20Partners%20and%20Lachy%20Groom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20%241%20trillion%20retail%20market%20has%20attracted%20global%20players%20like%20Amazon.com%20Inc.%20and%20Walmart%20Inc.-owned%20Flipkart%20Online%20Services%20Pvt%2C%20yet%20online%20sales%20still%20account%20for%20a%20minuscule%20share%20of%20that%20total.%20Zepto's%20sales%20in%20March%20grew%20about%20300%25%20from%20a%20year%20earlier%2C%20and%20its%20annual%20revenue%20has%20topped%20%24600%20million%2C%20Palicha%20said.%20Median%20delivery%20time%20is%2012%20minutes%2C%20and%20Zepto%20stores%20stock%20over%207%2C000%20products%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20skepticism%20around%20quick%20commerce%2C%26quot%3B%20Palicha%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20execute%20well%2C%20we%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20build%20an%20Amazon.com-type%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692954840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2F008cefog_zepto-founders_625x300_22_September_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fzepto-founders-zepto-unicorn-zomato-blinkit-how-two-20-year-olds-beat-grim-market-to-mint-indias-newest-unicorn-zepto-4328604%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zepto%2C%20an%20instant%20grocery%20startup%20founded%20by%20a%20duo%20of%20Stanford%20University%20dropouts%2C%20both%2020%2C%20raised%20fresh%20funds%20at%20a%20%241.4%20billion%20valuation%2C%20creating%20a%20rare%20Indian%20unicorn%20amid%20a%20gloomy%20venture%20funding%20climate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fzepto-founders-zepto-unicorn-zomato-blinkit-how-two-20-year-olds-beat-grim-market-to-mint-indias-newest-unicorn-zepto-4328604%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fzepto-founders-zepto-unicorn-zomato-blinkit-how-two-20-year-olds-beat-grim-market-to-mint-indias-newest-unicorn-zepto-4328604%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fzepto-founders-zepto-unicorn-zomato-blinkit-how-two-20-year-olds-beat-grim-market-to-mint-indias-newest-unicorn-zepto-4328604%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20police%20are%20investigating%20the%20deaths%20of%2088%20people%20linked%20to%20Canad