%2C%20Kashmiri%20artists%20added%20their%20own%20flourishes%20to%20the%20genre%2C%20attracting%20admirers%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20to%20their%20compositions.%20Photo%3A%20CNES%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20complex%20production%20process%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20masters%E2%80%99%20descendants%20have%20continued%20the%20work%2C%20particularly%20from%20the%20Shia%20community%2C%20forming%20two%20distinct%20communities%20involved%20in%20the%20craft%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekar-i-qalamdani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esakht-kaz%20turkhans%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(mould-makers)%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3En%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eaqash%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(artists).%20The%20mesh%20is%20created%20by%20using%20small%20pieces%20of%20paper%20and%20paper%20cuttings%2C%20which%20are%20soaked%20in%20water%20for%20periods%20stretching%20a%20month.%20Once%20the%20material%20is%20fit%20for%20moulding%2C%20a%20mixture%20of%20rice%20flour%20and%20water%20is%20used%20as%20an%20adhesive%20to%20give%20the%20shape%20and%20kept%20in%20sunlight%20until%20it%20becomes%20rigid%20to%20form%20the%20s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eakth%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eor%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Estructure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FDruCh-RPrl4%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Crafting%20Heritage%3A%20The%20Fading%20Artistry%20of%20Kashmiri%20Papier%20Mache%20(Part%201)%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20applying%20finishing%20touches%20on%20the%20structure%20using%20%3Cem%3Ek%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eur-kut%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20ignite%20rock%2C%20or%20baked%20rock%20%E2%80%93%20a%20process%20primarily%20handled%20by%20women.%20Once%20the%20structure%20is%20ready%2C%20the%20product%20is%20further%20worked%20upon%20by%20the%20na%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ekash%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewho%20makes%20colourful%20designs%20on%20the%20structure.%20First%2C%20a%20gold%20paper%20is%20used%20to%20give%20the%20structure%20a%20sparkling%20look%2C%20following%20which%20a%20variety%20of%20homemade%20colours%20are%20used%20to%20create%20the%20design.%20After%20applying%20varnish%2C%20the%20product%20is%20ready%20for%20exhibition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20some%20recurring%20themes%20and%20ideas%20in%20Kashmiri%20papier%20m%C3%A2ch%C3%A9%20that%20are%20meticulously%20portrayed%20in%20these%20%E2%80%9Coriginal%20masterpieces.%E2%80%9D%20These%20can%20be%20intricate%20calligraphic%20designs%20or%20flowery%20and%20naturalistic%20designs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArshid%20Hussain%2C%2037%2C%20explains%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20unified%20process%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cone%20defined%20by%20interconnectedness%2C%20as%20the%20project%20begins%20with%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20turkhan%2C%20who%20creates%20basic%20wooden%20structures%2C%20upon%20which%20the%20sakhtkar%20moulds%20the%20paper%20mesh%2C%20and%20the%20nakash%20finally%20creates%20design.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20intricate%20designs%20and%20labour-intensive%20processes%20has%20required%20significant%20amounts%20of%20expertise%20and%20patience.%20Both%20are%20only%20afforded%20to%20craftsmen%20who%20have%20engaged%20with%20the%20work%20for%20long%20durations.%20Despite%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia%2Freviving-traditions-now-learn-papier-mache-at-kashmir-university%2Fstory-igJ6bfgmHsPHaOypojdCsL.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egovernment%E2%80%99s%20efforts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20association%20with%20Kashmir%20University%20and%20the%20Kashmir%20handicraft%20department%2C%20to%20preserve%20the%20craft%20by%20introducing%20short%20term%20courses%2C%20there%20is%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20people%20to%20continue%20the%20craft%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20rising%20labour%20costs%20and%20a%20constrained%20domestic%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20ethnic%20background%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERooted%20in%20Iranian%20traditions%2C%20original%20works%20of%20papier%20mache%20can%20be%20identified%20in%20regions%20of%20Kashmir%20like%20Kamangar%20Pora%2C%20Hasan%20Abad%2C%20Rinwari%20%E2%80%93%20areas%20dominated%20by%20the%20Shia%20community.%20As%20such%2C%20the%20craft%20has%20endured%20in%20such%20regions%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20Kashmir%20being%20called%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIran-e-Sagheer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20little%20Iran.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzbY8W4d-dKg%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20As%20described%20by%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Muzafer%20Hussain%20(53)%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CShias%20were%20primarily%20involved%20in%20the%20craft%20of%20papier%20mache%2C%20while%20Sunnis%20showed%20interest%20in%20other%20crafts%20like%20carpet%20weaving%20and%20wood%20carving.%20Over%20time%2C%20our%20Sunni%20friends%20began%20learning%20the%20art%20of%20papier%20mache%20in%20various%20workshops.%20However%2C%20their%20involvement%20is%20mostly%20focused%20on%20the%20production%20of%20raw%20materials.%20Some%20Sunnis%20also%20had%20a%20role%20in%20designing%2C%20but%20they%20eventually%20left%20as%20they%20found%20better%20opportunities%20elsewhere.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fe02jfPF3jCE%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Crafting%20Heritage%3A%20The%20Fading%20Artistry%20of%20Kashmiri%20Papier%20Mache%20(Part%202)%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20interdependence%20of%20the%20two%20communities%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20Sunni%20community%20heavily%20involved%20in%20the%20exporting%20business%20of%20such%20products%2C%20both%20groups%20rely%20on%20each%20other%20to%20facilitate%20the%20sale%20of%20these%20crafted%20goods%2C%20thus%20creating%20a%20form%20of%20camaraderie.%20Yet%2C%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20craft%20is%20deeply%20intertwined%20with%20the%20cultural%20identity%20of%20the%20Shia%20community%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzbY8W4d-dKg%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Muzafer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEngaging%20in%20this%20craft%20allows%20us%20to%20freely%20fulfill%20our%20religious%20obligations%2C%20something%20that%20may%20not%20be%20as%20feasible%20in%20other%20professions.%20It%20becomes%20a%20form%20of%20Sufi%20art%20where%20we%20find%20solace%20and%20spiritual%20fulfillment%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20our%20homes%2C%20detached%20from%20the%20distractions%20of%20the%20outside%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20I%20changed%20my%20surname%20from%20Kamangahr%20to%20Joo%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0explains%20Muzafer%20Hussain%20Joo%2C%20while%20elaborating%20about%20the%20fraternity%20with%20the%20two%20sub-ethnic%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20He%20further%20remarks%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20our%20Sunni%20friends%20began%20learning%20the%20art%20of%20papier%20mache%20in%20various%20workshops.%20Now%2C%20there%20is%20a%20village%20called%20Nowpora%20in%20Srinagar%20where%20approximately%20500%20artists%20are%20engaged%20in%20papier%20mache.%20However%2C%20their%20inv