0the%20toll%20it%20takes%20on%20artisans%2C%20as%20they%20sit%20steady%20for%20elongated%20periods%20of%20time%20while%20carefully%20working%20on%20perfecting%20each%20piece%20product%20for%20days%20at%20end.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20sit%20for%2012%20hours%20and%20it%20takes%20a%20heavy%20toll%20on%20our%20eyes%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20says%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20we%20cannot%20use%20a%20chair%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMysir%20Khan%20further%20explains%20the%20adverse%20health%20effects%20of%20the%20painstaking%20process%20of%20designing%20elegant%20and%20sophisticated%20papier%20mache%20artefacts.%20He%20says%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20in%20workshops%20provides%20a%20positive%20experience%20for%20us%20as%20artists.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20become%20increasingly%20common%20for%20artists%20to%20work%20in%20isolation%2C%20which%20can%20take%20a%20toll%20on%20their%20mental%20health.%20The%20constant%20focus%20and%20intricate%20details%20involved%20can%20strain%20our%20eyes.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20cannot%20work%20continuously%20for%20extended%20periods%20and%20need%20to%20take%20breaks%20every%20hour%20to%20rest%20our%20eyes%20and%20prevent%20fatigue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%201990s%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20steady%20erosion%20in%20the%20local%20market%20for%20such%20goods.%20Owing%20to%20political%20unrest%2C%20marketplaces%20were%20shut%20down%20frequently%2C%20dwindling%20the%20already%20meager%20incomes%20of%20the%20artists.%20As%20the%20number%20of%20tourists%20started%20to%20decline%2C%20the%20fear%20of%20continued%20turbulence%20discouraged%20the%20artists%20from%20entering%20this%20line%20of%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20illustrating%20the%20dying%20demand%20of%20the%20authentic%20motifs%2C%20Parvaiz%20Ahmad%20Naqash%2C%20an%20exporter%20in%20Papier%20Mache%2C%20notes%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COne%20notable%20example%20of%20this%20shift%20in%20demand%20is%20the%20closure%20of%20the%20renowned%20showroom%2C%20Suffering%20Moses%2C%20which%20specialised%20in%20authentic%20papier%20machie%20products.%20Over%20time%2C%20customers%20lost%20interest%20in%20these%20traditional%20items.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20evening%20sun%20goes%20down%2C%20Mirza%20Ghulam%20also%20begins%20to%20wrap%20his%20work%20for%20the%20day.%20The%20meticulous%20design%20begins%20to%20take%20shape%20on%20the%20canvas%2C%20but%20the%20work%20is%20nowhere%20near%20finished.%20As%20he%20eyes%20his%20creation%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbSc7ESpn1RI%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20laments%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CM%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eost%20of%20the%20commercial%20products%20nowadays%20have%20defamed%20the%20art%20of%20papier%20mache.%20As%20this%20work%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20patience%2C%20younger%20generations%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20time%20or%20energy%20to%20devote%20to%20this%20endeavour.%20What%20is%20left%20in%20the%20markets%20are%20imitations%20of%20the%20real%20art%2C%20that%20is%20not%20durable%20or%20of%20quality%20work%2C%20but%20suits%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20market.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20and%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%2C%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%20and%20Humanities%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20Ishfaq%20Ahmad%20Wani%20is%20a%20Contributing%20Research%20Analyst%20with%20CNES%20Visual%20Storyboards.%20Tavleen%20Kaur%20and%20Hima%20Trisha%20are%20Senior%20Research%20Analysts%20and%20CNES%20Visual%20Storyboards%20team%20leads.%20Yashovardhan%20Chaturvedi%20and%20Anousha%20Singh%20are%20Research%20Analysts%20with%20CNES.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENames%20of%20all%20respondents%20have%20been%20changed%20to%20protect%20their%20identity%20and%20maintain%20anonymity.%20The%20authors%20would%20like%20to%20especially%20thank%20Dr.%20Rekha%20Pachauri%20and%20Dr.%20Meera%20Shirodkar%20for%20their%20assistance%20with%20field%20work%2C%20interviews%20and%20in%20the%20audio-video%20documentation%20of%20the%20study.%20Without%20their%20support%2C%20this%20study%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20photographs%20are%20credited%20to%20them%20and%20Ishfaq%20Ahmad%20Wani.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20part%20one%20of%20a%20three-part%20series%20undertaken%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvisualstoryboardscnes.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVisual%20Storyboard%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20initiative%20of%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%2C%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20Visual%20Storyboards%E2%80%99%20work%20can%20be%20accessed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvisualstoryboardscnes.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20For%20this%20project%2C%20please%20find%20all%20video%20essays%20published%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPL8RbNXSvnr8QZ9EhRXib4M7c1l1FYMBM-%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692952245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25133937%2FScreenshot-2023-08-25-at-1.38.50-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fpapier-mache-kashmir-art-dying%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20craft%20carried%20with%20it%20a%20form%20of%20prestige%20for%20artists%2C%20who%20would%20devote%20long%20periods%20of%20time%20and%20effort%20over%20