20the%20upcoming%20G20%20summit%2C%20which%20will%20held%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20for%20three%20days%20-%208-10%20September.%20Special%20CP%20(Traffic)%20SS%20Yadav%20said%20that%20restrictions%20will%20be%20put%20in%20place%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20area%2C%20since%20the%20summit%20will%20be%20held%20at%20the%20newly-built%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20convention%20centre%20in%20Delhi's%20Pragati%20Maidan%20under%20India's%20presidency.%20The%20restrictions%20will%20be%20put%20in%20place%20from%20the%20night%20of%20September%207%20and%20remain%20in%20place%20till%20September%2010%2C%20said%20Mr%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20live%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20area%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20move%20freely%2C%20but%20those%20coming%20from%20other%20districts%20of%20Delhi%2C%20or%20tourists%20from%20other%20places%2C%20will%20have%20to%20show%20valid%20hotel%20bookings%20to%20enter%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fg20-summit-whats-open-whats-closed-in-delhi-all-you-need-to-know-4325756%5C%22%3EG20%20Summit%3A%20What's%20Open%2C%20What's%20Closed%20In%20Delhi%3F%20All%20You%20Need%20To%20Know%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20traffic%20police%20has%20also%20warned%20people%20to%20not%20visit%20markets%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20area%20on%20September%208%2C%209%20and%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20will%20also%20keep%20cargo%20trucks%20out%20of%20Delhi%20for%20three%20days%2C%20said%20Mr%20Yadav.%20They%20will%20be%20diverted%20to%20the%20Eastern%20and%20Western%20peripheral%20expressways.%20But%20vehicles%20with%20permission%20or%20carrying%20important%20cargo%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0Interstate%20buses%20will%20also%20be%20allowed%20entry%20into%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20restriction%20on%20vehicles%20deployed%20in%20emer