%20to%20flow%20in%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20will%20require%20multilateral%20(global)%20financial%20institutions%20to%20be%20restructured%20and%20redesigned.%20They%20were%20made%20in%20the%20post-World%20War%20II%20period...%20when%20there%20was%20no%20climate%20change%20and%20no%20SDG%20(sustainable%20development%20goal).%20Therefore%20these%20need%20to%20be%20changed...%20to%20confront%20climate%20change%20and%20bring%20in%20new%20instruments%2C%20like%20blended%20finance%2C%20first%20loss%20guarantees%20and%20credit%20enhancement%20to%20allow%20private%20capital%20to%20flow%20in%20to%20Global%20South%20nations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EG20%20Presidency%20Big%20Chance%20For%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kant%20also%20spoke%20about%20India%20hosting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fg20-summit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EG20%20presidency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20comes%20at%20a%20point%20when%20the%20world%20faces%20multiple%20challenges%20and%20gives%20New%20Delhi%20a%20'huge%20opportunity'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne-third%20of%20the%20world%20is%20in%20recession....%2075%20nations%20face%20debt%20crisis...%20100%20million%20people%20have%20lost%20jobs...%20there%20is%20a%20food%20crisis%2C%20a%20fuel%20crisis%20and%20a%20climate%20crisis.%20And%20the%20geopolitical%20crisis%20in%20Europe%20(exacerbated%20by%20Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine)%20continues%20for%20over%20a%20year-and-a-half.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20in%20every%20crisis%2C%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20opportunity%20and%2C%20for%20India%2C%20this%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20do%20what%20Prime%20Minister%20(Narendra%20Modi)%20called%20for%20-%20to%20be%20inclusive%2C%20decisive%2C%20action-oriented%20and%20ambitious%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20India%20assumes%20presidency%20of%20the%20G20%20when%20its%20own%20economy%20is%20on%20a%20strong%20upward%20trend.%20%26quot%3B...%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India%20has%20accelerated%20its%20pace%20of%20growth.%20India%20is%20the%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20and%2C%20in%202027%2C%20will%20be%20the%20third%20largest%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20government%20think-tank%20NITI%20Aayog%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EIndia%20To%20Focus%20On%20Global%20South%20At%20G20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-brings-g20-spotlight-back-on-real-issues-of-global-south-s-jaishankar-4115574%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20G20%20during%20its%20presidency%20will%20be%20on%20the%20Global%20South%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20includes%20poor%20countries%20from%20Africa%2C%20Asia%20and%20South%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20as%20early%20as%20last%20year%2C%20that%20while%20it%20is%20understandable%20that%20some%20of%20this%20focus%20is%20on%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20this%20could%20not%20obfuscate%20the%20real%20concerns%20and%20pain%20points%20of%20the%20Global%20South.%20He%20said%20there%20were%20countries%20who%20could%20not%20feed%20their%20people%2C%20are%20running%20short%20of%20fuel%20and%20had%20suffered%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692948780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F9b83i31_amitabh-kant-ndtv-650_650x400_25_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-summit-india-amitabh-kant-b20-summit-global-south-to-drive-2-3-of-worlds-growth-big-chance-for-india-g20-sherpa-amitabh-kant-4328285%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Global%20South%20-%20nations%20with%20developing%2C%20less%20developed%20or%20under-developed%20economies%20-%20will%20drive%20two-thirds%20of%20global%20economic%20growth%2C%20G20%20Sherpa%20Amitab