hey%20decided%20to%20deliver%20the%20baby%20there.%20Now%2C%20the%20baby%20and%20mother%20are%20doing%20well%20at%20the%20Community%20Health%20Centre%20in%20Khanapur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20acknowledged%20that%20there%20was%20no%20road%20connectivity%20to%20Thulasipet%20village%20after%20a%20bridge%20was%20washed%20away%20in%20floods%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20invited%20tenders%20for%20building%20a%20new%20bridge%2C%20but%20no%20one%20has%20responded%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692948120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Foa0keou8_telangana-woman-_625x300_25_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Ftelangana-woman-delivers-baby-on-road-as-ambulance-runs-out-of-fuel-4328239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20pregnant%20woman%20delivered%20her%20baby%20on%20the%20side%20of%20a%20road%20in%20a%20remote%20area%20of%20Telangana's%20Nirmal%20district%20after%20she%20was%20carried%20across%20a%20stream%20while%20in%20labour.%20The%20ambulance%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20pick%20her%20up%20had%20run%20out%20of%20diesel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Ftelangana-woman-delivers-baby-on-road-as-ambulance-runs-out-of-fuel-4328239%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Ftelangana-woman-delivers-baby-on-road-as-ambulance-runs-out-of-fuel-4328239%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Ftelangana-woman-delivers-baby-on-road-as-ambulance-runs-out-of-fuel-4328239%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20has%20taken%20away%20India's%20land%2C%20says%20Rahul%3B%20BJP's%20retort%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692948117000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsi