findia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fhrithik-roshan-lauds-naseeruddin-shahs-short-film-featuring-saba-azad%2Farticleshow%2F103050914.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%3A%20The%20moment%20India's%20lunar%20rover%20Pragyaan%20stepped%20out%20for%20Moonwalk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692947490000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F14D1F%2Fproduction%2F_130897258_belly.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66613688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20space%20agency%20Isro's%20new%20footage%20shows%20Chandrayaan-3's%20rover%20Pragyaan%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A139%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66613688%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66613688.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66613688.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Tomahto%2C%20Tomayto%20-%20Soaring%20Prices%2C%20Government%20In%20Denial%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWearing%20a%20garish%20gold%20necklace%20to%20parliament%20is%20allowed.%20A%20string%20of%20sparkling%20De%20Beers%20diamonds%20will%20also%20do.%20But%2C%20heaven%20help%20the%20Member%20of%20parliament%20who%2C%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20wore%20a%20garland%20of%20tomatoes%20(and%20ginger)%20as%20a%20unique%20form%20of%20protest%20against%20sky-rocketing%20prices.%20Wearing%20tomatoes%20as%20jewellery%20was%20powerful%20imagery.%20However%2C%20the%20MP%20was%20admonished%20for%20doing%20so.%20In%20the%20season%20of%20Privilege%20Notices%20and%20suspensions%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20was%20let%20off%20with%20a%20warning.%20I%20still%20have%20not%20figured%20out%20what%20his%20crime%20was.%20Which%20rule%20did%20he%20break%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDerailing%20RBI's%20Projections%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%20came%20confirmation%20of%20what%20was%20largely%20expected%20-%20a%20huge%20jump%20in%20retail%20and%20food%20inflation%20figures.%20Over%20the%20last%20two%20months%2C%20prices%20of%20vegetables%2C%20spices%20and%20several%20other%20food%20items%20have%20hit%20a%20high.%20The%20year-on-year%20increase%20in%20the%20Consumer%20Food%20Price%20Index%20in%20June%20was%204.5%25%2C%20which%20leaped%20to%20a%20whopping%2011.5%25%20in%20July.%20This%20was%20primarily%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20inflation%20rate%20for%20vegetables%2C%20which%20witnessed%20a%20sharp%20increase%20and%20rose%20to%2037%25%20year-on-year.%20The%20inflation%20rate%20surged%20to%2013%25%20for%20cereals%20and%20products%2C%20and%2013.3%25%20for%20pulses%20and%20products.%20For%20milk%20and%20products%2C%20it%20increased%20to%208.3%25.%20Spices%20had%20surged%2021%25.%20Overall%2C%20in%20the%20food%20and%20beverages%20segment%2C%20the%20increase%20was%20over%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurging%20food%20prices%20have%20had%20a%20domino%20effect%2C%20materially%20changing%20India's%20inflation%20outlook.%20India's%20retail%20inflation%20rose%20to%207.4%25%20year-on-year%20in%20July%2C%20surpassing%20the%20upper%20limit%20of%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)'s%20tolerance%20band%20of%206%25.%20This%20trend%20has%20led%20to%20the%20RBI%20upwardly%20revising%20India's%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20inflation%20rate%20for%20the%20year%20from%205.1%25%20to%205.4%25.%20The%20RBI%20Governor%20has%20even%20warned%20that%20policymakers%20will%20have%20to%20stand%20ready%20to%20go%20beyond%20keeping%20a%20watchful%20eye%2C%20and%20deploy%20policy%20instruments%20if%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20In%20Denial%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20recently%20concluded%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20this%20columnist%20had%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20provide%20the%20month-wise%20trend%20in%20the%20average%20prices%20of%20vegetables.%20On%2021%20July%2C%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20the%20question%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Consumer%20Affairs%2C%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution%20gave%20a%20surprising%20and%20misleading%20answer.%20The%20last%20row%20of%20the%20table%20annexed%20to%20the%20answer%20quoted%20prices%20of%20the%20'rare'%20commodity%20that%20was%20bewildering.%20Titled%20%26quot%3BAll-India%20Monthly%20Average%20Retail%20Prices%20of%20Tomato%20(Rs%2Fkg)%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20figures%20for%202023%20were%3A%2024.72%20(January)%2C%2023.45%20(February)%2C%2023.32%20(March)%2C%2023.16%20(April)%2C%2023.61%20(May)%2C%20and%2032.58%20(June).%20What%20is%20this%20government%20smoking!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETomatoes%20were%20hovering%20around%20the%20double%20century-mark.%20As%20we%20write%20this%2C%20the%20prices%20have%20softened%20-%20but%20nowhere%20near%20what%20was%20presented%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20parliament.%20This%20columnist%20visited%20three%20vegetable%20markets%20each%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Kolkata%20for%20a%20reality%20check.%20It%20is%20a%20good%20case%20to%20bring%20a%20breach%20of%20privilege%20motion%20against%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Consumer%20Affairs%2C%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution%20for%20misleading%20Parliament.%20(Spare%20the%20feeble%20Minister%20of%20State.%20His%20seniors%20have%20turned%20this%20into%20an%20art%20form).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20real-time%20wages%20are%20falling%20and%20unemployment%20is%20rising.%20The%20tomato%2C%20as%20a%20visual%20mnemonic%2C%20summarises%20the%20situation.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20Portuguese%20were%20the%20first%20to%20introduce%20the%20tomato%20in%20India%20in%20the%20early%2016th%20century.%20Referred%20to%20as%20the%20yellow%20or%20pink%20apple%2C%20natives%20called%20it%20the%20red%20berry%20or%20the%20%3Cem%3Evilayti%20begun%3C%2Fem%3E%20(foreign%20brinjal).%20It%20acquired%20this%20name%20as%20it%20was%20mainly%20consumed%20by%20the%20British%20%3Cem%3E(vilayti)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20French%20used%20to%20call%20tomatoes%3Cem%3E%20pommes%20d'amour%3C%2Fem%3E%20(love%20apples).%20Going%20by%20current%20market%20prices%2C%20perhaps%20the%20most%20apt%20name%20for%20tomatoes%20was%20coined%20by%20the%20Italians%2C%20who%20used%20to%20call%20tomatoes%20%3Cem%3Epomi%20d'oro%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20meaning%20golden%20apples.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP.S.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fepaper.timesgroup.com%2Fcartoons%2Fr-k-laxman%2Fcommon-man%2Fcartoon-on-business-economy%2F1659639013614%5C%22%3EThis%20comic%20strip%3C%2Fa%3E%20created%20by%20RK%20Laxman%20thirty%20years%20ago%20is%20as%20relevant%20today%20as%20it%20was%20back%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7DhDJmR27qo%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Opinion%3A%20Tomahto%2C%20Tomayto%20-%20Soaring%20Prices%2C%20Government%20In%20Denial%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Research%3A%20Anushtup%20Haldar%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692947460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fl9mmhl08_tomatoes-generic-afp_625x300_28_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftomahto-tomayto-soaring-prices-government-in-denial-4328182%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Surging%20food%20prices%20have%20had%20a%20domino%20effect%2C%20materially%20changing%20India's%20inflation%20outlook.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%2