Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20US%20and%20UK%20trade%20representatives%20who%20are%20in%20Jaipur%20for%20the%20G20%20trade%20meet%20want%20the%20joint%20communique%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20adverse%20impact%20of%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20could%20pose%20a%20challenge%20to%20India%20in%20forging%20consensus%20on%20the%20language%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fus-uk-insist-on-recognising-adverse-impact-of-russias-war-on-ukraine-at-g20-trade-meet%2Farticle67231512.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20Businessline%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20G20%20Trade%20and%20Investment%20Ministers%E2%80%99%20Meeting%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20the%20US%20Trade%20Representative%20Katherine%20Tai%20and%20UK%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20International%20Trade%20Kemi%20Badenoch%20both%20spoke%20about%20the%20economic%20impact%20that%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20is%20having%20on%20the%20world%2C%20highlighting%20food%20inflation%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20progress%20in%20the%20five%20trade%20and%20investment%20areas%2C%20including%20MSME%20integration%20and%20GVCs%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Businessline%20said%20the%20forging%20consensus%20on%20the%20language%20for%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20could%20pose%20a%20challenge%20for%20India%20as%20the%20G20%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETai%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20%E2%80%9Ctrade%20for%20growth%20and%20prosperity%20cannot%20be%20discussed%E2%80%9D%20without%20acknowledging%20the%20serious%20impact%20of%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cpremeditated%20and%20unprovoked%E2%80%99%E2%80%99%20war.%20She%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Frussia-pulls-out-of-ukraine-grain-deal-heres-what-this-means%5C%22%3Ecollapse%20of%20the%20Black%20Sea%20Grain%20Initiative%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Cprovided%20a%20lifeline%20for%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20worldwide%20facing%20hunger%20and%20spiralling%20food%20costs%20by%20enabling%20the%20delivery%20of%2020%20million%20tonnes%20of%20grain%20to%20lower%20and%20middle-income%20countries%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20call%20on%20Russia%20to%20reverse%20its%20decision%2C%20to%20resume%20negotiations%2C%20and%20to%20extend%2C%20expand%2C%20and%20fully%20implement%20the%20Initiative%20immediately%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20people%20who%20depend%20on%20Ukrainian%20grain.%20Beyond%20this%20action%2C%20Russia%20must%20end%20its%20unjustified%20war%20of%20aggression%20against%20Ukraine%20and%20withdraw%20all%20of%20its%20forces%20from%20Ukraine%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tai%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20disagreement%20over%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20among%20G20%20countries%20could%20hamper%20the%20chances%20of%20a%20joint%20communique%20at%20the%20Trade%20and%20Investment%20meet%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20UK%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20International%20Trade%20Badenoch%20admitted%20that%20forging%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20joint%20communique%20is%20going%20to%20be%20difficult.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20our%20perspective%2C%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20what%20we%20are%20really%20emphasising%2C%20especially%20as%20today%20is%20the%20Ukrainian%20day%20of%20independence%2C%20just%20how%20significant%20an%20impact%20that%20war%20has%20had%20on%20UK%20trade%2C%20on%20European%20trade%20and%20on%20global%20trade%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EBusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20key%20G20%20meetings%2C%20of%20finance%20ministers%20and%20central%20bank%20governors%20in%20Gandhinagar%3B%20and%20of%20foreign%20ministers%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%2C%20have%20already%20failed%20to%20issue%20joint%20communiques%20because%20of%20differences%20over%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%3C