n%20Parliament.%20This%20will%20significantly%20weaken%20Modi's%20stranglehold%20on%20India's%20federal%20govt.%20I%20expect%20a%20democratic%20revival%20in%20India%E2%80%A6I%20could%20be%20foolish%2C%20but%20I%20think%20democracy%20will%20flourish%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20Soros%20saw%20India%20to%20be%20happy%20and%20healthy%20in%20the%20UPA%201%20and%20UPA%202%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20Hindenburg%20report%20Adani%20stocks%20badly%20tumbled%2C%20a%20political%20storm%20erupted%2C%20opposition%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20forced%20complete%20washout%20of%20winter%20session%20of%20Parliament%2C%20all%20kinds%20of%20allegations%20were%20made%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%20by%20its%20known%20critics%20and%20political%20rivals%2C%20but%20as%20the%20time%20passed%20people%20and%20investors%20saw%20through%20the%20possible%20game%20in%20that%20foreign-originated%20report%2C%20Adani%20stocks%20gained%20upward%20momentum%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20committee%20led%20by%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20AM%20Sapre%20on%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20issue%20came%20to%20a%20conclusion%20that%20%26quot%3Bprima%20facie%20no%20regulatory%20failure%20on%20part%20of%20the%20SEBI%20around%20the%20allegation%20of%20price%20manipulation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20Soros'%20wishes%20couldn't%20get%20the%20flight%20path%20trajectory%20he%20wanted.%20There%20is%2C%20thus%2C%20this%20informed%20speculation%20the%20OCCRP%20was%20coming%20out%20with%20%26quot%3BHindenburg%202.0%26quot%3B%20to%20try%20and%20cause%20further%20political%20and%20economic%20upheaval%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20proved%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20that%20they%20time%20their%20report%20with%20some%20important%20events%20in%20India's%20calendar.%20Let's%20see%20why%20the%20current%20timing%20is%20important.%20But%20before%20that%20a%20bit%20of%20backgrounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20a%20six-member%20expert%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20committee%20stated%20that%20there%20was%20evidence%20of%20a%20build-up%20in%20short%20positions%20on%20Adani%20Group%20stocks%20ahead%20of%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.%20Suspicious%20trading%20was%20observed%20on%20the%20part%20of%20six%20entities.%20Of%20these%2C%20four%20are%20FPIs%2C%20one%20body%20corporate%20and%20one%20individual.%20Some%20news%20reports%20suggest%20that%20on%20further%20investigation%2C%20the%20number%20of%20such%20entities%20have%20gone%20up.%20It%20suggested%20that%20SEBI%20ought%20to%20be%20probing%20such%20actions%20under%20securities%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%20is%20expected%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Aug.%2029.%20It%20is%20nobody's%20case%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20verdict%20can%20be%20influenced%20by%20some%20media%20or%20other%20privately%20funded%20reports%2C%20but%20such%20reports%20do%20create%20a%20negative%20buzz%20and%20give%20some%20additional%20talking%20points%20to%20the%20petitioner's%20lawyers%20in%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20less%20than%20a%20fortnight%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20be%20hosting%20the%20G20%20summit%20meeting%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Raising%20political%20dust%20or%20adverse%20economic%2Fstock%20market%20report%20wouldn't%20be%20in%20the%20best%20interests.%20PM%20Modi%20and%20India%20in%20recent%20years%20have%20gained%20great%20stature%20in%20the%20global%20high%20table.%20India%20through%20its%20hard%20work%20in%20various%20sectors%20is%20trying%20overtime%20to%20go%20higher.%20Modi%20has%20already%20declared%20that%20in%20his%20third%20term%20India%20will%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%20That%20surely%20does%20not%20go%20well%20with%20India%20and%20Modi%20baiters%20in%20sections%20of%20supposed%20Western%20influence%20groups.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20INDIA%20block%20is%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Aug.%2031.%20It%20has%20been%20proven%20that%20the%20Opposition%20picks%20up%20anything%20and%20everything%2C%20real%2C%20half-truth%20or%20manufactured%2C%20in%20its%20bid%20to%20target%20the%20Modi%20government.%20The%20Soros%20Open%20society-funded%20Hindenburg%202.0%2C%20if%20it%20comes%2C%20would%20be%20instantly%20used%20as%20ammunition.%20More%20so%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20newly%20formed%20alliance%20is%20showing%20signs%20of%20conflict%20and%20contradiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20worthwhile%20to%20recall%20what%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20that%20he%20was%20not%20sure%20if%20election%20season%20had%20started%20in%20India%2C%20but%20for%20sure%20it%20had%20started%20in%20New%20York%20and%20London.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202024%20elections%20has%20moved%20even%20closer.%20Soros%20and%20his%20men%20for%20sure%20are%20working%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692945300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-01%2Flefga968_george-soros-wef-_625x300_24_January_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsoros-backed-occrp-getting-ready-for-a-hit-job-on-india-4328098%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Just%20as%20'India%20on%20the%20Moon'%20celebrations%20were%20in%20full%20throttle%20in%20the%20country%20and%20congratulatory%20messages%20pouring%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20on%20a%20milestone%20achieved%20by%20Indian%20scientists%20at%20ISRO.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsoros-backed-occrp-getting-ready-for-a-hit-job-on-india-4328098%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsoros-backed-occrp-getting-ready-for-a-hit-job-on-india-4328098%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsoros-backed-occrp-getting-ready-for-a-hit-job-on-india-4328098%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-UP%20Minister%20Jailed%20For%20Poet's%20Murder%20To%20Be%20Freed.%20What%20Was%20The%20Case%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20release%20of%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20minister%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%2C%20who%20was%20convicted%20in%20the%20sensational%202003%20murder%20of%20poet%20Madhumita%20Shukla%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhumita-shukla-murder-case-ex-up-minister-amarmani-tripathi-accused-of-murdering-poetess-to-be-released-from-jail-4327683%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20to%20be%20released%20from%20jail%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Tripathi%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20also%20to%20be%20released%2C%20have%20been%20serving%20a%20life%20term%20since%202007%20but%20will%20be%20freed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20'good%20conduct'%20in%20prison%2C%20the%20UP%20government%20said%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shukla's%20sister%20had%20appealed%20the%20release%20of%20Tripathi%20and%20his%20wife.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20while%20declining%20to%20interfere%20in%20Tripathi's%20release%2C%20has%20sought%20a%20reply%20from%20the%20UP%20government%20in%20eight%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUP%20Prisons%20Minister%20Dharamveer%20Prajapati%20had%20earlier%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSuch%20releases%20happen%20on%20basis%20of%20how%20prisoners%20conduct%20themselves%20in%20jail.%20Files%20are%20moved%20and%20acted%20upon%20only%20after%20orders%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20(Yogi%20Adityanath)%20and%20Governor%20(Anandiben%20Patel).%20This%20is%20how%20things%20are%20progressing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20a%20minister%20in%20Mayawati's%20government%2C%20Tripathi%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20boss'%20right-hand%20man%20and%20had%20initially%20claimed%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20gruesome%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20denials%20were%20up-ended%2C%20though%2C%20after%20a%20DNA%20test%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20indicated%20the%20child%20Ms%20Shukla%20was%20carrying%20when%20she%20was%20shot%20dead%20was%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EMs%20Shukla's%20Family%2C%20Others%20Respond%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shukla's%20sister%20has%20refused%20to%20comment%20on%20Tripathi's%20release%20beyond%20stating%20the%20Governor%20must%20have%20%26quot%3Btaken%20a%20call%20based%20on%20government%20files%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BCannot%20comment%20on%20the%20Governor's%20decision%20but%20I%20can%20say%20that%20the%20Governor%20takes%20a%20call%20based%20on%20government%20files%20and%20does%20so%20after%20deep%20contemplation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20also%20questioned%20Tripathi's%20release%20and%20has%20mocked%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20claiming%20he%20is%20being%20released%20as%20the%20BJP%20%26quot%3Bneeds%26quot%3B%20him%20for%20next%20year's%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*Under%20what%20rules%20are%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20and%20his%20wife%20being%20released%3F%20It%20seems%20BJP's%20Yogi%20-%20Modi%20model%20has%20become%20stale%2C%20so%20they%20need%20Amarmani.%20They%20may%20even%20end%20up%20needing%20Mukhtar%20Ansari.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20am%20sure%2C%20whichever%20criminal%20in%20jail%20BJP%20needs%20for%202024%20election%2C%20all%20will%20be%20bailed%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20SP%20spokesperson%20Manoj%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Was%20The%20Madhumita%20Shukla%20Murder%20Case%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhumita%20Shukla%2C%20a%20fiery%20poet%2C%20was%20murdered%20on%20May%209%2C%202003.%20Her%20body%20was%20found%20at%20her%20home%20in%20Lucknow's%20Nishatganj%20area.%20Ms%20Shukla%20was%2024%20years%20old%20and%20allegedly%20Tripathi's%20lover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Famarmani-tripathi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmarmani%20Tripathi%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20then%20a%20four-time%20MLA%20with%20links%20to%20various%20political%20parties%20and%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20influence%2C%20which%20was%20why%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20transferred%20the%20case%20from%20Lucknow%20to%20Dehradun%20after%20Ms%20Shukla's%20family%20feared%20Tripathi%20may%20interfere%20with%20the%20judicial%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shukla%20was%20pregnant%20when%20she%20died%20and%20the%20father%20was%20said%20to%20be%20Tripathi%2C%20something%20confirmed%20after%20forensics%20examinations%20by%20the%20CBI.%20However%2C%20such%20was%20Tripathi's%20unsavoury%20influence%20then%20that%20few%20dared%20speak%20against%20him%2C%20never%20mind%20make%20such%20serious%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22taof97og%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ftaof97og_amarmani-tripathi_625x300_25_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEx-UP%20minister%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20had%20denied%20any%20connection%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Madhumita%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20in%20October%202007%2C%20Ms%20Shukla's%20sister%20seemed%20to%20emphasise%20the%20fear%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20evoked%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20not%20an%20ordinary%20person.%20That%20is%20all%20I%20can%20say.%26quot%3B%20When%20asked%20if%20she%20was%20scared%20of%20Tripathi%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20say%20anything%20else%20about%20the%20case%20at%20this%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shukla's%20sister%20also%20spoke%20of%20%26quot%3Bnever-ending%26quot%3B%20threats%20against%20the%20family%2C%20stating%20these%20continued%20even%20after%20the%20case%20was%20transferred%20out%20of%20UP%20and%20to%20