-under-bankruptcy-law-says-ceo-karan-adani%2F97768007%5C%22%3EKaraikal%3C%2Fa%3E%20ports)%2C%20it%20also%20buys%20firms%20outright%20from%20their%20promoters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpectacularly%20profitable%20after%20the%20first%20ten%20or%20so%20years%2C%20concessions%20are%20not%20always%20available%20for%20sale.%20And%20yet%2C%20Adani%20has%20managed%20to%20buy%20as%20many%20as%20six%20ports%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20Some%20sales%20have%20been%20concluded%20despite%20Adani%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Gangavaram%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2023%2F02%2Fap-governments-sale-of-its-equity-share-in-gangavaram-port-to-adani-ports-caused-a-huge-loss-to-public-exchequer-special-audit-called-for%2F%5C%22%3Eas%20alleged%20by%20former%20Union%20revenue%20secretary%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20valuing%20the%20assets%20conservatively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20some%20cases%20saw%20a%20coincidental%20overlap%20between%20stake%20sale%20and%20actual%20or%20alleged%20state%20action.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Navayuga%2C%20the%20promoter%20of%20Krishnapatnam%20port%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fandhra-govt-retrieves-4700-acres-from-krishnapatnam-infratechs-sez%2Farticleshow%2F71683465.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Efound%20itself%20in%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20crosshairs%3C%2Fa%3E%20soon%20after%20the%20government%20of%20Y.S.%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20came%20to%20power.%20Reddy%20acted%20against%20business%20houses%20that%20had%20won%20contracts%20during%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20tenure%20of%20his%20political%20rival%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20of%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP).%20In%20the%20case%20of%20GVK%2C%20whose%20promoters%20were%20investigated%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freepressjournal.in%2Fbusiness%2Fmumbai-airport-was-handed-over-to-adani-after-snatching-away-from-gvk-rahul-gandhi%5C%22%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20using%20his%20agencies%20to%20hasten%20the%20sale%20of%20Mumbai%20airport%20to%20the%20Adanis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20pointed%20accusation%20has%20prompted%20strong%20denials%20by%20the%20Adanis%20and%20GVK.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20after%20Gandhi%20spoke%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20airport%20sale%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20GVK%20Group%E2%80%99s%20vice-chairman%20Sanjay%20Reddy%20issued%20a%20statement%20saying%20he%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fthere-was-no-pressure-from-adani-group-to-sell-mumbai-airport-gvks-sanjay-reddy-1188988.html%5C%22%3Enot%20been%20coerced%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20Gangavaram%2C%20though%20industry%20executives%20and%20at%20least%20two%20state%20government%20officials%20and%20a%20relative%20of%20the%20port%E2%80%99s%20promoter%20D.V.S.%20Raju%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20whom%20asked%20that%20their%20identity%20not%20be%20revealed%20%E2%80%93%20spoke%20of%20state%20government%20interest%20as%20a%20factor%20in%20the%20sale%2C%20both%20Adani%20and%20Raju%20denied%20there%20had%20been%20any%20official%20involvement%20in%20the%20deal.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20allegations%20are%20false%20and%20baseless%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Adani%20group%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20emailed%20to%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20in%20response%20to%20a%20questionnaire%20that%20cited%20some%20of%20these%20accusations.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%2C%20despite%20not%20being%20true%2C%20such%20allegations%20are%20being%20rehashed.%E2%80%9D%20As%20for%20Raju%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20it%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20emphasise%20that%20this%20decision%20was%20made%20independently%2C%20without%20any%20external%20pressure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20backstory%20of%20Gangavaram%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20time%2C%20the%20land%20around%20Gangavaram%20must%20have%20been%20scenic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shore%20here%20seems%20to%20inch%20almost%20imperceptibly%20towards%20the%20sea.%20Before%20the%20port%20came%2C%20local%20fisherfolk%20walked%20through%20fields%20and%20coconut%20groves%20to%20their%20boats.%20As%20they%20walked%20towards%20the%20sea%2C%20small%20hills%20stood%20to%20their%20left%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20the%20city%20of%20Visakhapatnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201994%2C%20the%20state%20government%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20port%20on%20the%20site%20of%20two%20villages%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGangavaram%2C_Visakhapatnam%5C%22%3EGangavaram%20and%20Dibbapalem%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20idea%20had%20been%20doing%20the%20rounds%20for%20a%20while.%20%E2%80%9CVisakhapatnam%20Port%20wanted%20to%20set%20Gangavaram%20as%20a%20satellite%20port%20and%20shift%20polluting%20cargo%20like%20coal%20%E2%80%93%20which%20went%20to%20local%20industries%20like%20the%20Vizag%20Steel%20Plant%20%E2%80%93%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20union%20leader%20in%20Visakhapatnam.%20%E2%80%9CVizag%20Steel%20Plant%20wanted%20to%20set%20up%20a%20private%20port%20at%20Gangavaram%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20however%2C%20was%20liberalising.%20State-directed%20capitalism%20was%20on%20the%20back%20foot.%20These%20proposals%20%E2%80%93%20from%20state-owned%20entities%20%E2%80%93%20went%20nowhere.%20Instead%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20at%20the%20time%2C%20took%20over%20the%20project%2C%20saying%20Gangavaram%20would%20be%20developed%20as%20a%20state%20port%2C%20using%20India%E2%80%99s%20brand%20new%20Public%20Private%20Partnership%20(PPP)%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20first%20time%20Adani%20evinced%20interest%20in%20Gangavaram.%20In%202001%2C%20a%20consortium%20led%20by%20Adani%20Exports%20(which%20would%20later%20become%20Adani%20Enterprises)%20participated%20in%20the%20tender.%20It%20lost%20to%20the%20only%20other%20rival%20bidder%20%E2%80%93%20a%20consortium%20led%20by%20D.V.S.%20Raju%2C%20a%20former%20senior%20executive%20at%20IT%20giant%20Satyam%20and%20founder%20of%20VisualSoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWork%20began%20in%202005.%20When%20local%20villagers%20protested%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Fbloodbath-at-gangavaram%2Farticleshow%2F1466613.cms%5C%22%3Ethe%20state%20bit%20down%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CProtestors%20were%20jailed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20union%20leader.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20violence%20at%20this%20time.%20Two%20villagers%20died%20in%20police%20firing.%E2%80%9D%20That%20was%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20port%20then%20came%20up%20as%20planned%20and%20operations%20started%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Ftransportation%2Fshipping-%2F-transport%2Fadani-ports-in-talks-with-warburg-to-buy-out-latters-pe-shareholding-in-gangavaram-port%2Farticleshow%2F48011318.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EApril%202009%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Given%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Flogistics%2Fgangavaram-port-handles-100th-capesize-vessel%2Farticle20562822.ece1%5C%22%3Edeep%20draft%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20seabed%20off%20India%E2%80%99s%20east%20coast%20drops%20steeply%20just%20beyond%20the%20shore%20%E2%80%93%20Capesize%20vessels%20could%20dock%20at%20Gangavaram.%20Given%20its%20proximity%20to%20the%20Vizag%20Steel%20Plant%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20mineral-rich%20states%20like%20Odisha%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20port%20found%20itself%20importing%20and%20exporting%20iron%20ore%20and%20coal%20cargo%20%E2%80%93%20and%20growing%20rapidly.%20Built%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Feconomy-policy%2Fcm-inaugurates-gangavaram-port-109071300026_1.html%5C%22%3ERs%201%2C850%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20port%E2%80%99s%20first%20phase%20hit%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fcompanies%2Fgangavaram-port-hopes-to-break-even-in-3-yrs-111083100037_1.html%5C%22%3Ecash%20break-even%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202010-11.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20the%20way%2C%20it%20began%20attracting%20buyers.%20%E2%80%9C(Stock%20trader)%20Rakesh%20Jhunjhunwala%20tried%20around%202012%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20retired%20senior%20official%20at%20Vizag%20Port%20Trust.%20%E2%80%9CDVS%20(Raju)%20refused%20at%20the%20time.%20He%20quoted%20a%20very%20high%20premium.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20Adani%20tried%20again.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20travelled%20down%20to%20Andhra%20with%20his%20son%20Karan%20Adani%20and%20aide%20Rajesh%20Naithani%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20senior%20executive%20at%20a%20south%20Indian%20port%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20time%20around%2C%20Raju%20was%20more%20open%20to%20an%20exit.%20His%20health%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20very%20good%20and%20so%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20monetise%20at%20a%20good%20valuation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20talks%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsonprojects.com%2Fnews%2Fno-further-move-by-adani-to-take-over-gangavarm-port%5C%22%3Ebroke%20down%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20reasons%20are%20unclear.%20Neither%20Raju%20nor%20the%20Adani%20Group%20responded%20to%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%99s%20question%20about%20these%20talks.%20According%20to%20the%20port%20executive%2C%20a%20disagreement%20over%20payment%20schedules%20was%20to%20blame.%20According%20to%20a%20former%20official%20in%20the%20state%20ports%20department%2C%20however%2C%20a%20difference%20in%20valuation%20was%20the%20trigger.%20%E2%80%9CAdani%20wanted%20to%20pay%20around%20Rs%205%2C600-Rs%205%2C900%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20for%20Raju%2C%20he%20wanted%20%5Bmore%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20stayed%20calm%20for%20the%20next%20three%20years.%20And%20then%2C%20two%20big%20developments%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPrelude%20to%20an%20acquisition%2C%20a%20crucial%20rule%20change%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20model%20port%20concession%20agreement%20has%20a%20grey%20zone%2C%20said%20the%20retired%20Vizag%20Port%20Trust%20official.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20concessionaires%20can%20be%20replaced%20if%20they%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20default%20on%20a%20loan%2C%20the%20agreement%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20clarify%20if%20concessions%20can%20be%20sold%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20why%2C%20he%20said%20this%20was%20probably%20an%20omission.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20the%20drafters%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20imagine%20an%20outcome%20where%20anyone%20would%20want%20to%20sell.%20For%20the%20first%20ten%20years%20of%20its%20life%2C%20the%20project%20would%20have%20high%20debt.%20In%20the%20subsequent%20years%2C%20you%20make%20a%20killing.%20Why%20would%20anyone%20sell%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20concessions%20should%20not%20be%20tradable%2C%20the%20port%20executive%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20concession%20is%20given%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20qualifications.%20In%20such%20a%20set-up%20%E2%80%93%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20that%20all%20natural%20resources%20have%20to%20be%20awarded%20through%20bids%20to%20avoid%20windfall%20gains%20%E2%80%93%20the%20government%20has%20to%20re-bid.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202018%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20changed%20the%20rules%20for%20port%20concessions%2C%20providing%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetail.aspx%3FPRID%3D1515181%5C%22%3E%20an%20exit%20route%20to%20developers%20by%20way%20of%20divesting%20their%20equity%20up%20to%20100%25%20after%20completion%20of%202%20years%20from%20the%20commercial%20operation%20date%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20that%20the%20government%20said%20at%20the%20time%20was%20that%20this%20change%20was%20made%20%E2%80%9Ckeeping%20in%20view%20the%20experience%20gained%20in%20managing%20PPP%20projects%20in%20port%20sector%20during%20the%20last%20twenty%20years%20and%20to%20obviate%20the%20problems%20being%20faced%20on%20account%20of%20certain%20provisions%20in%20the%20existing%20MCA.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20wrote%20to%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal%2C%20Union%20minister%20for%20ports%2C%20shipping%20and%20waterways%2C%20asking%20him%20about%20the%20logic%20behind%20this%20amendment.%20This%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20he%20responds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEnter%20Jagan%20as%20CM%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20consequential%20development%20followed%20in%20May%202019.%20On%20May%2030%2C%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20businessman-politician%20son%20of%20former%20state%20chief%20minister%20Y.S.%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%20came%20to%20power%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fys-jagan-mohan-reddy-longest-padayatra-praja-sankalpa-yatra-ysr-congress-5530862%2F%5C%22%3Eone-year%20march%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20state%20which%20positioned%20him%20as%20a%20mass%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F30143541%2FUntitled-design-80.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F30143541%2FUntitled-design-80.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F30143541%2FUntitled-design-80-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F30143541%2FUntitled-design-80-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-646366%5C%22%20height%3D