Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20considering%20whether%20Adani%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20smoothly%20acquire%20Krishnapatnam%20%E2%80%93%20or%20Gangavaram%20in%20its%20entirety%20%E2%80%93%20if%20the%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20government%20had%20not%20acted%20the%20way%20it%20did.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20these%20two%20ports%2C%20even%20assuming%20the%20state%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20looking%20to%20expressly%20benefit%20anyone%2C%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20Adani%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20Aurobindo%20Realty%20%E2%80%93%20was%20the%20biggest%20gainer%20from%20the%20increasingly%20Darwinian%20politics%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20MIAL%2C%20the%20unfortunately%20timed%20crackdown%20on%20GVK%20came%20from%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(M.%20Rajshekhar%20is%20an%20independent%20reporter%20studying%20corruption%2C%20oligarchy%20and%20the%20political%20economy%20of%20India%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%99%3Ci%3Es%20environment.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20author%20of%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FDespite-State-India-Lets-People%2Fdp%2F8194879019%2F%5C%22%3EDespite%20the%20State%3A%20Why%20India%20Lets%20Its%20People%20Down%20and%20How%20They%20Cope%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ci%3EReporting%20for%20this%20project%20was%20supported%20by%20Pulitzer%20Center)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAppendix%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Response%20to%20The%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20Questionnaire%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThank%20you%20for%20approaching%20us%2C%20please%20find%20herewith%20our%20response%20to%20your%20query%20as%20appended%20%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20allegations%20are%20false%20and%20baseless.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%2C%20despite%20not%20being%20true%2C%20such%20allegations%20are%20being%20rehashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20decades%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20has%20p