C%20Adani%20emerged%20as%20a%20potential%20buyer%20to%20acquire%20Warburg%E2%80%99s%20entire%20stake%20%5Bi.e.%2031.5%25%5D%20and%20even%20hired%20investment%20bank%20Macquarie%20Capital%20to%20advise%20on%20the%20stake%20acquisition%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ECapital%20Quest%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20210304152801%2Fhttps%3A%2Fthecapitalquest.com%2F2021%2F03%2F04%2Fwarburg-pincus-to-score-12-fold-return-from-long-standing-india-bet%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20deal%20fell%20through%20owing%20to%20a%20valuation%20mismatch.%E2%80%9D%20Nevertheless%2C%20six%20years%20later%2C%20Adani%20was%20able%20to%20acquire%20100%25%20of%20Gangavaram%20for%20Rs%206%2C200%20crore.%20This%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20port%E2%80%99s%20capacity%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Ftransportation%2Fshipping-%2F-transport%2Fadani-ports-in-talks-with-warburg-to-buy-out-latters-pe-shareholding-in-gangavaram-port%2Farticleshow%2F48011318.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ewhich%20was%2030%20million%20tonnes%20in%202015%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20doubled%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbesindia.com%2Farticle%2Fhidden-gems-2019%2Fgangavaram-port-a-lesson-in-location-location-location%2F54853%2F1%5C%22%3E60%20million%20tonnes%20by%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbesindia.com%2Farticle%2Fhidden-gems-2019%2Fgangavaram-port-a-lesson-in-location-location-location%2F54853%2F1%5C%22%3E%202019%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20its%20dampening%20effect%20on%20the%20economy%20might%20have%20played%20a%20role%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20why%20Warburg%20settled%20on%20a%20lower%20valuation%2C%20setting%20a%20benchmark%20price%20that%20Raju%20and%20%E2%80%93%20more%20controversially%20%E2%80%93%20the%20AP%20state%20government%20subsequently%20went%20by.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20sent%20a%20questionnaire%20to%20the%20equity%20firm%20on%20June%2029%2C%202023%2C%20and%20will%20update%20this%20story%20if%20and%20when%20their%20answer%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24180456%2Fimage-1243.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24180456%2Fimage-1243.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24180456%2Fimage-1243-300x78.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24180456%2Fimage-1243-1024x267.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669639%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22313%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGangavaram%20Port.%20Photo%3A%20Adani%20Ports%20website%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20good%20deal%20for%20buyer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGangavaram%20port%20had%20posted%20an%20EBITDA%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fcompanies%2Fapsez-to-acquire-31-5-stake-in-gangavaram-port-for-rs-1-954-crore-121030301314_1.html%5C%22%3E%20Rs%20634%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20FY20.%20The%20sale%20price%20of%20a%20company%20is%20a%20multiple%20of%20EBIDTA%20%E2%80%93%20a%20measure%20of%20how%20much%20it%20earns%20every%20year%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20multiple%20a%20measure%20of%20the%20number%20of%20years%20the%20buyer%20needs%20to%20recoup%20his%20purchase%20price.%20With%20Adani%20paying%20Rs%206%2C200%20crore%2C%20the%20deal%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaniports.com%2FNewsroom%2FMedia-Releases%2FAPSEZ-fully-unlocks-eastern-hinterland%5C%22%3Eenterprise%20value%2FEBITDA%20multiple%3C%2Fa%3E%20stood%2C%20by%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20own%20calculations%2C%20at%20a%20relatively%20low%208.8%20%E2%80%93%20a%20measure%20of%20how%20good%20a%20deal%20this%20was%20for%20the%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20relatively%20low%20multiple%20is%20now%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20petition%20in%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20high%20court%2C%20with%20the%20petitioner%20claiming%20it%20was%20well%20below%20global%20benchmarks%20for%20port%20acquisitions.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20May%202019%2C%20when%20PSA%2C%20Polish%20Development%20Fund%20and%20IFM%20Global%20Infrastructure%20Fund%20acquired%20100%25%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feurobuildcee.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2F27006-dct-gdansk-sold-for-usd-13-bln%5C%22%3E%20DCT%20Gdansk%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Macquarie%20Infrastructure%20and%20Real%20Assets%2C%20they%20paid%20an%20enterprise%20value%2FEBIDTA%20multiple%20of%2016%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20petition%20filed%20in%202021%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Freedsvsbreddy.blogspot.com%2F2012%2F07%2Fcv-of-mr-satya-bhupal-reddy-vaiza.html%5C%22%3ESatya%20Bhupal%20Reddy%20Vaiza%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20an%20NGO%20called%20REEDS.%20%E2%80%9CSimilarly%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-ooil-m-a-macquarie-idUSKCN1S604S%5C%22%3EOrient%20Overseas%20International%3C%2Fa%3E%20sold%20its%20container%20terminal%20to%20Macquarie%20Infrastructure%20and%20Real%20Assets%2C%20it%20did%20so%20at%20a%20multiple%20of%20over%2020%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20PIL%2C%20which%20is%20challenging%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20sell%20its%20own%20stake%20of%2010%25%20in%20Gangavaram%20to%20Adani%20without%20inviting%20bids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20within%20India%2C%20the%20deal%E2%80%99s%20enterprise%20value%2FEBITDA%20multiple%20stood%20on%20the%20lower%20side.%20Just%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20Adani%20had%20acquired%20Andhra%E2%80%99s%20private%20sector%20Krishnapatnam%20Port%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaniports.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FPorts%2FInvestor%2FInvestor-Downloads%2FInvestors-Presentation%2FAPSEZ-Investor-Presentation---KPCL-Final.pdf%5C%22%3ERs%2013%2C572%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20a%20multiple%20of%2010.2%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20it%20carrying%20debt%20of%20Rs%206%2C212%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2C%20at%2064%20million%20tons%2C%20having%20similar%20capacity%20as%20Gangavaram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20Gangavaram%20was%20debt-free%20and%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaniports.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FPorts%2FInvestor%2FInvestor-Downloads%2FInvestors-Presentation%2FGPL-APSEZ-Stake-Acquisition-Presentation-March-3.pdf%5C%22%3Ecash%20balance%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaniports.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2FProject%2FPorts%2FInvestor%2FInvestor-Downloads%2FInvestors-Presentation%2FGPL-APSEZ-Stake-Acquisition-Presentation-March-3.pdf%5C%22%3ERs%20570%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time%20of%20acquisition.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvijayawada%2Fpil-challenges-sale-of-govts-stake-in-gannavaram-port%2Farticleshow%2F86124015.cms%5C%22%3EPIL%2C%20which%20is%20still%20before%20the%20court%2C%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20state%20government%20did%20not%20follow%20prescribed%20norms%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20valuing%20its%20share%2C%20nor%20the%20value%20of%20the%20land%20that%20Adani%20would%20now%20get%20effective%20control%20over.%20The%20port%20concession%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fandhra-pradesh-government-adani-gift-gangavaram-port-privatisation-opposed-unions-2021%2Farticle35251137.ece%5C%22%3Ealso%20included%201%2C800%20acres%20of%20nearby%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20given%20by%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20when%20he%20was%20chief%20minister.%20Going%20by%20market%20rates%2C%20the%20PIL%20claimed%2C%20that%20land%20was%20now%20worth%20at%20least%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELengthy%20counter%20affidavits%20were%20filed%20by%20the%20state%20government%20(the%20Adani%20group%20was%20not%20named%20as%20a%20respondent)%20between%20September%202021%20and%20January%202022%20disputing%20the%20petitioner%E2%80%99s%20claims%20on%20the%20value%20of%20the%20land%20and%20the%20port%20as%20a%20whole.%20The%20last%20time%20the%20court%20took%20up%20the%20matter%20was%2C%20however%2C%20in%20December%202021.%20Now%2C%20a%20former%20revenue%20secretary%20in%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2023%2F02%2Fap-governments-sale-of-its-equity-share-in-gangavaram-port-to-adani-ports-caused-a-huge-loss-to-public-exchequer-special-audit-called-for%2F%5C%22%3Ewritten%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India%20noting%20what%20he%20alleges%20are%20anomalies%20in%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20sale%20of%20its%20Gangavaram%20stake%20to%20the%20Adanis%20and%20demanded%20an%20audit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20better%20understand%20the%20Gangavaram%20deal%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20met%20port%20promoters%2C%20spoke%20to%20senior%20executives%20in%20ports%20and%20other%20infrastructure%20companies%20acquired%20by%20Adani%20and%20their%20peers%20in%20industry%2C%20the%20relatives%20and%20associates%20of%20promoters%20whose%20firms%20have%20been%20acquired%20by%20Adani%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20secretary%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20former%20bureaucrats%20in%20mid-%20and%20senior%20positions%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20including%20those%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20planning%20and%20ports%20department%3B%20and%20the%20owners%20of%20firms%20that%20dealt%20with%20Gangavaram%20%E2%80%93%20like%20those%20importing%20coal%20through%20the%20port%2C%20and%20those%20offering%20shipping%20logistics%2C%20as%20well%20as%20activists%20and%20trade%20union%20leaders%20working%20in%20Gangavaram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2C%20about%2045%20interviews%20were%20conducted.%20Subsequently%2C%20detailed%20sets%20of%20questions%20were%20emailed%20to%20all%20the%20%3Cem%3Edramatis%20personae%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Adani%20Group%3B%20D.V.S.%20Raju%3B%20Warburg%20Pincus%2C%20C.%20Sridhar%20of%20Navayuga%20Engineering%20Company%3B%20K.%20Muralidharan%20(formerly%20at%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Maritime%20Board)%3B%20KPMG%2C%20which%20valued%20Gangavaram%3B%20the%20Union%20ministry%20for%20ports%20and%20shipping%3B%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20CM%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-rise-reading-list%5C%22%3EA%20Journalistic%20History%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Adani%20growth%20machine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20observers%20of%20corporate%20India%2C%20the%20sprawling%20Adani%20group%20is%20something%20of%20a%20black%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20in%20long-gestation%2C%20low-margin%20sectors%20like%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%93%20and%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F923201%2Ffrom-2014-to-2019-how-the-adani-group-funded-its-expansion%5C%22%3E%20much%20lower%20group%20EBITDA%20than%20peers%20like%20Reliance%20and%20Tata%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20group%20has%20grown%20furiously.%20Not%20only%20did%20it%20direct%20cash%20into%20existing%20businesses%20and%20loss-making%20arms%2C%20it%20simultaneously%20acquired%20rival%20firms%20%E2%80%93%20through%20buy-outs%20like%20Gangavaram%20and%20asset%20sales%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20bankruptcy%20courts%20%E2%80%93%20and%20announced%20large%20forays%20into%20sunrise%20sectors%20like%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20renewables%20manufacturing%20and%20defence.%20Most%20recently%2C%20it%20acquired%20a%20large%20media%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia-telecom%2Findias-ndtv-founders-transfer-most-their-stake-adani-2022-12-23%2F%5C%22%3ENDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20added%20to%20its%20considerable%20presence%20in%20the%20cement%20sector%20by%20buying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-plans-4-5-bn-cement-bet-after-sanghi-acquisition-11691087953827.html%5C%22%3ESanghi%20Cements%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20January%2C%20when%20Hindenburg%20Research%20released%20its%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Fadani%2F%5C%22%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20the%20spotlight%20has%20turned%20onto%20the%20financial%20arrangements%20that%20have%20enabled%20this%20dizzyingly%20rapid%20expansion.%20Hindenburg%20alleges%20Adani%20has%20used%20a%20clutch%20of%20offshore%20entities%20to%20push%20up%20its%20share%20prices%2C%20a%20charge%20the%20company%20denies.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20the%20company%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F923201%2Ffrom-2014-to-2019-how-the-adani-group-funded-its-expansion%5C%22%3Epledged%20shares%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20raise%20debt.%20It%20has%20used%20international%20bonds%20to%20mop%20up%20additional%20debt.%20Those%20borrowed%20sums%20are%20used%20for%20not%20just%20capex%20but%2C%20as%20Hindenburg%20charged%2C%20also%20to%20smoothen%20out%20earnings%20%E2%80%93%20and%20to%20launch%20new%20businesses%20(Adani%20has%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F923201%2Ffrom-2014-to-2019-how-the-adani-group-funded-its-expansion%5C%22%3Eborrowed%20funds%20as%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20new%20businesses).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20expert%20panel%20tasked%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20look%20into%20some%20of%20the%20questions%20raised%20by%20Hindenburg%20concluded%20that%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20to%20sustain%20the%20charge%20of%20stock%20manipulation.%20It%20also%20concluded%20that%20there%20had%20been%20no%20regulatory%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbecause-of-repealed-provisions-sebi-hit-opaque-structure-wall-while-investigating-adani-sc-panel%5C%22%3Ethough%20repealed%20provisions%20had%20hampered%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20ability%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20investigate%20what%20it%20noted%20were%20%E2%80%9Copaque%20structures%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20was%20accused%20of%20using.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20Hindenburg%2C%20some%20investors%20have%20highlighted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Fcorporate%2Fstory%2Fgqgs-rajiv-jain-to-explain-rs-15446-cr-investment-in-adani-group-to-australian-investors-this-week-372584-2023-03-07%5C%22%3Ethe%20strength%20of%20Adani%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Fcorporate%2Fstory%2Fgqgs-rajiv-jain-to-explain-rs-15446-cr-investment-in-adani-group-to-australian-investors-this-week-372584-2023-03-07%5C%22%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3Es%20underlying%20assets.%20Supporting%20the%20group%20with%20both%20cash%20flows%20and%20hard%20assets%2C%20acquisitions%20account%20for%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20those%20assets.%20As%20Hindenburg%20Research%20says%20in%20its%20report%2C%20%E2%80%9C(APSEZ)%20is%E2%80%A6%20the%20only%20listed%20(Group)%20entity%20which%20seems%20capable%20of%20consistently%20generating%20substantive%20positive%20cash%20flow%3A%20approximately%20INR%2052%20billion%20(US%20%24640%20million)%20as%20of%2031%20March%2C%202022.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECentral%20to%20APSEZ%E2%80%99s%20cash%20flow%20is%20the%20array%20of%20strong%20assets%20the%20company%20has%20assembled.%20Take%20Adani%20Ports.%20Its%20first%20port%20came%20up%20in%201998%20(Mundra%2C%20Gujarat).%20In%20the%20next%2014%20years%2C%20it%20added%20two%20more%20ports%2C%20both%20in%20Gujarat%20%E2%80%93%20Dahej%20(2010)%20and%20Hazira%20(2012).%20Thereafter%2C%20its%20growth%20has%20been%20quicksilver.%20It%20added%20Mormugao%20(2013)%3B%20acquired%20Dhamra%20from%20L%26amp%3BT%20and%20Tata%20(2014)%3B%20set%20up%20Tuna%20Tekra%20and%20acquired%20Katupalli%20from%20L%26amp%3BT%20(2015)%3B%20signed%20Ennore%20(2018)%3B%20bagged%20Vizhinjam%20(2019)%3B%20acquired%20Krishnapatnam%20(2020)%3B%20bought%20Dighi%20through%20India%E2%80%99s%20bankruptcy%20courts%20and%20acquired%20Gangavaram%20(2021).%20As%20this%20article%20was%20being%20written%2C%20the%20conglomerate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Ftransportation%2Fshipping-%2F-transport%2Fnclt-approves-adani-ports-and-sezs-takeover-of-karaikal-port%2Farticleshow%2F99184118.cms%5C%22%3Ebagged%20the%20port%20at%20Karaikal%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20bankruptcy%20proceedings.%20In%20all%2C%20then%2C%20the%20Adani%20group%20has%2013%20ports%20%E2%80%93%20of%20which%2C%20six%20have%20been%20acquired%20%E2%80%93%20in%20India.%20It%20also%20has%20Haifa%20in%20Israel%20and%20a%20terminal%20in%20Colombo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F04110729%2Fkaraikal.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22866%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F04110729%2Fkaraikal.png%20647w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F04110729%2Fkaraikal-300x195.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-646934%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22562%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKaraikal%20Port.%20Photo%3A%20karaikalport.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20acquisitions%20are%20significant%20given%20the%20history%20of%20the%20sector.%20The%20first%20generation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20ports%20%E2%80%93%20like%20Kandla%2C%20Paradeep%20and%20JNPT%20%E2%80%93%20were%20built%20by%20the%20state.%20The%20second%20generation%20%E2%80%93%20like%20Mundra%2C%20Gangavaram%20and%20Krishnapatnam%20%E2%80%93%20were%20built%20after%20liberalisation%20as%20public-private%20partnerships.%20Reflecting%20both%20cronyism%20and%20the%20need%20to%20attract%20private%20sector%20participation%20in%20what%20were%20untested%20and%20risky%20greenfield%20projects%2C%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20offered%20generous%20incentives%C2%A0%20to%20promoters.%20If%20a%20project%20matured%20and%20took%20off%20after%20its%20difficult%20gestation%20period%2C%20the%20promoter%20stood%20to%20make%20a%20handsome%20profit.%20As%20would%20the%20government%2C%20which%20retained%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnapatnam%E2%80%99s%20agreement%20with%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20not%20only%20gave%20its%20promoters%2C%20the%20Navayuga%20group%2C%20an%20exclusive%20zone%20%E2%80%93%20in%20which%20no%20other%20port%20could%20come%20up%20%E2%80%93%20of%2030%20kilometres%20on%20either%20side%2C%20it%20also%20pegged%20the%20concession%20fee%20payable%20to%20the%20state%20at%20just%202.6%25%20(of%20gross%20income)%20for%20the%20first%2030%20years.%20As%20the%20PIL%20filed%20in%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20high%20court%20says%2C%20the%20average%20revenue%20share%20offered%20by%20other%20ports%2Fterminals%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20eastern%20shore%20stands%20at%2033.15%25.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20revenue%20share%20offered%20in%20the%20case%20of%20already%20established%20major%20ports%20was%20as%20high%20as%2052%25%20since%20there%20is%20already%20established%20infrastructure%2C%20ready%20customer%20and%20infrastructural%20linkages%20with%20minimal%20risk%20to%20the%20bidder%2Fterminal%20operator%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petitioners%20wrote%20in%20their%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202015%20CAG%20report%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fwebroot%2Fuploads%2Fdownload_audit_report%2F2015%2FUnion_Performance_Commercial_PPP_Report_49_2015.pdf%5C%22%3EPPP%20projects%20in%20major%20ports%3C%2Fa%3E%20contains%20similar%20numbers.%20In%202005%2C%20Dubai%20Ports%20International%20bagged%20a%20tender%20to%20build%20and%20run%20a%20container%20transshipment%20terminal%20at%20Cochin%20Port%20Trust%20by%20offering%20a%20revenue%20share%20of%2033.3%20percent%20of%20gross%20revenues.%20In%202009%2C%20JNPT%20awarded%20the%20project%20to%20build%20a%20container%20terminal%20to%20PSA%20Mumbai%20Investment%20after%20it%20promised%20a%20revenue%20share%20of%2050.828%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGangavaram%E2%80%99s%20terms%20are%20the%20same%20as%20those%20of%20Krishnapatnam.%20%E2%80%9CIts%20initial%20concession%20%5Bin%202002-03%5D%20was%20given%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20DPR%2C%E2%80%9D%20or%20detailed%20project%20report%2C%20a%20senior%20executive%20at%20a%20private%20port%20in%20southern%20India%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%20Defending%20the%20low%20revenue%20share%20for%20the%20government%20of%202.1%25%20that%20was%20written%20into%20the%20initial%20concession%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20asset.%20Also%2C%20these%20concessions%20were%20signed%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20economy%20was%20growing%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98Hindu%E2%80%99%20rate%20of%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20Adani%20acquired%20Gangavaram%2C%20however%2C%20the%20situation%20had%20changed.%20The%20port%20had%20become%20a%20mature%20concession%20with%20ongoing%20operations%2C%20an%20established%20market%20position%2C%20monopolistic%20cash%20flows%20and%20vastly%20transformed%20surroundings%20as%20an%20industrial%20area%20developed%20around%20the%20port.%20And%20yet%2C%20by%20acquiring%20the%20concession%20through%20Gangaravam%2C%20Adani%20will%20give%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20a%20revenue%20share%20of%20just%202.1%20per%20cent%20till%202039%2C%20i.e.%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cag.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fdownload_audit_report%2F2013%2FAndhra_Pradesh_economic_sector_report_3_2013_chapter_5.pdf%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cag.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fdownload_audit_report%2F2013%2FAndhra_Pradesh_economic_sector_report_3_2013_chapter_5.pdf%5C%22%3Ethe%20first%2030%20years%20of%20the%20Concession%20Period%2C%20and%20at%20double%20the%20rate%20for%20%5B%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cag.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fdownload_audit_report%2F2013%2FAndhra_Pradesh_economic_sector_report_3_2013_chapter_5.pdf%5C%22%3Etwo%5D%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cag.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fdownload_audit_report%2F2013%2FAndhra_Pradesh_economic_sector_report_3_2013_chapter_5.pdf%5C%22%3E%20extended%20spells%20of%2010%20years%20each.%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economics%20of%20the%20deal%20needs%20to%20be%20underlined.%20According%20to%20the%20Adani%20Ports%20website%2C%20Gangavaram%20can%20handle%2060%20million%20tons%20of%20cargo%20in%20a%20year.%20If%20Adani%20charges%20Rs%20300%20per%20ton%20of%20cargo%2C%20it%20will%20generate%20a%20top%20line%20of%20Rs%201%2C800%20crore.%20If%20Gangavaram%20settles%20at%20similar%20operating%20margins%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20Adani%20Ports%20(44.22%25)%20%E2%80%93%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fnews-cm%2Fadani-port-spurts-on-acquiring-controlling-stake-in-gangavaram-port-from-dvs-raju-family-121032300327_1.html%5C%22%3E%20its%20EBIDTA%20margins%20in%20FY21%20stood%20at%2059%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20it%20will%20make%20Rs%20795.9%20crore%20as%20operating%20profit.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20revenue%20share%2C%20however%2C%20will%20stand%20at%20just%20Rs%2037.8%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEffectively%2C%20then%2C%20the%20Adani%20group%20has%20acquired%20a%20mature%20asset%20on%20greenfield%20terms.%20Profits%20that%20should%20have%20gone%20to%20the%20initial%20risk-taking%20entrepreneur%20or%20the%20state%20government%20%E2%80%93%20which%20could%20have%20earned%20a%20fatter%20revenue%20share%20by%20re-tendering%20the%20concession%20as%20a%20mature%20PPP%20%E2%80%93%20flow%20to%20Adani%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbengal-murshidabad-adani-power-transmission%5C%22%3EIn%20Bengal%2C%20Villagers%20Say%20Adani%20Power%E2%80%99s%20Transmission%20Tower%20Ravaged%20a%20Century-Old%20Orchard%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20centrality%20of%20concessions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20they%20become%20highly%20profitable%20after%20the%20first%20ten%20or%20so%20years%2C%20matured%20concessions%20are%20not%20always%20up%20for%20sale.%20And%20yet%2C%20Adani%20has%20picked%20up%20six%20ports%20in%20just%20nine%20years.%20It%20has%20done%20so%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Gangavaram%2C%20without%20paying%20a%20high%20EV%2FEBIDTA%20multiple%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20while%20the%20company%20paid%20Rs%206%2C200%20crore%20for%20Gangavaram%2C%20after%20the%20acquisition%2C%20at%20a%20multiple%20of%2020%2C%20the%20port%20could%20arguably%20be%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20Rs%2012%2C680%20crore.%20By%20pledging%20these%20shares%2C%20the%20group%20could%20conceivably%20raise%20more%20cash%20than%20what%20it%20had%20paid%20Raju%20%E2%80%93%20and%20then%20repay%20those%20loans%20through%20Gangavaram%E2%80%99s%20cash%20flows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cproven%20its%20expertise%20in%20designing%2C%20building%20and%20managing%20world%20class%20infrastructure%20projects%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9Cin%20addition%20to%20greenfield%20projects%2C%20the%20Group%20has%20also%20relied%20on%20strategic%20acquisitions%20to%20expand%20its%20business.%20Our%20business%20expansion%20decisions%20emerge%20from%20a%20careful%20evaluation%20of%20the%20state%20of%20the%20potential%20acquisition%2C%20its%20prospects%20for%20growth%20and%20its%20synergies%20with%20our%20existing%20operations%2C%20through%20fair%2C%20transparent%20and%20well-established%20business%20processes.%20These%20are%20business%20transactions%20handled%20professionally%2C%20with%20mutual%20respect%20and%20trust.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20this%20article%2C%20%E2%80%98Adani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20Inside%20the%20Company%E2%80%99s%20Growth%20Machine%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-inside-the-companys-growth-machine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20read%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20The%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20questionnaire%20sent%20as%20part%20of%20the%20reporting%20for%20this%20series%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-inside-the-companys-growth-machine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eread%20in%20full%20in%20the%20second%20part.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.%20Rajshekhar%20is%20an%20independent%20reporter%20studying%20corruption%2C%20oligarchy%20and%20the%20political%20economy%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%3Cem%3Es%20environment.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20author%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FDespite-State-India-Lets-People%2Fdp%2F8194879019%2F%5C%22%3EDespite%20the%20State%3A%20Why%20India%20Lets%20Its%20People%20Down%20and%20How%20They%20Cope%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Cem%3EReporting%20for%20this%20project%20was%20supported%20by%20Pulitzer%20Center.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20story%20was%20edited%20at%2010%3A10%20am%20on%20August%2025%2C%202023%20to%20add%20the%20date%20on%20which%20The%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20questionnaire%20to%20Warburg%20Pincus%20was%20sent%20and%20at%20noon%20to%20include%20a%20para%20from%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20The%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20questions%2C%20which%20has%20been%20carried%20in%20full%20in%20Part%202%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692930789000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F09100312%2Ffile7oqadvldvf8n9qdh4kn-1-1187073-1675331608.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-the-inorganic-strategy-behind-the-purchase-of-gangavaram-port%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20weeks%20and%20months%20after%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20has%20repeatedly%20alluded%20to%20the%20robust%20health%20of%20its%20underlying%20assets.%20How%20it%20came%20to%20acquire%20some%20of%20them%20is%20worth%20a%20deeper%20look.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-the-inorganic-strategy-behind-the-purchase-of-gangavaram-port%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Rhetoric%2C%20Routine%20and%20Ruse%20of%20a%20Regime%3A%20The%20Case%20of%20NCERT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F18121235%2FSocial-Science-India-and-the-Contemporary-World-I-class-ix-NCERT.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20National%20Council%20of%20Education%20Research%20and%20Training%20(NCERT)%20has%20been%20in%20the%20news.%20In%20July%202023%2C%20an%20NCERT%20notification%20announced%20a%2019-member%20panel%20to%20finalise%20textbooks%20and%20learning%20materials%20for%20schools%20under%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECelebrity%20mathematicians%2C%20musicians%2C%20sports%20personnel%20along%20with%20a%20host%20of%20big%20names%20constitute%20the%20committee.%20Whether%20due%20process%20was%20followed%20or%20not%20is%20not%20quite%20the%20point%2C%20for%20this%20has%20long%20been%20replaced%20by%20a%20culture%20of%20ordinances.%20Both%20due%20process%20and%20accountability%2C%20whether%20in%20matters%20of%20state%20functioning%20or%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20knowledge%20production%2C%20are%20dispensable.%20This%20announcement%2C%20therefore%2C%20needs%20to%20be%20placed%20in%20a%20larger%20context%20of%20a%20certain%20approach%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20design%20and%20messaging%2C%20that%20the%20regime%20has%20mastered.%20g.%20For%2C%20as%20we%20are%20told%2C%20everything%20is%20about%20%E2%80%98perceptions%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20details%20are%20dispensable.%20That%20in%20a%20country%20as%20diverse%20and%20unequal%20as%20ours%2C%20most%20members%20of%20the%20committee%20come%20from%20a%20certain%20demography%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20matter.%20That%20almost%20all%20are%20aligned%20to%20the%20government%20also%20does%20not%20matter.%20Many%20of%20them%20are%20accomplished%20in%20their%20own%20field%20but%20there%20seems%20little%20in%20evidence%20of%20their%20familiarity%20with%20pedagogic%20issues.%20While%20few%20of%20them%20have%20excellent%20academic%20credentials%20in%20their%20field%20(mathematics%20in%20specific)%20one%20wonders%20whether%20they%20have%20engaged%20with%20the%20unequal%20conditions%20of%20Indian%20school%20education%2C%20persistent%20drop%20out%20rates%20and%20dismal%20learning%20outcomes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fncert-history-textbooks-mughals-india%5C%22%3E%20If%20NCERT%20Has%20its%20Way%2C%20the%20Study%20of%20Indian%20History%20Will%20Move%20Entirely%20Outside%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20use%20of%20such%20names%20is%20clearly%20not%20about%20hands-on%20expertise%20but%20about%20invoking%20authority.%20Can%20one%20ask%20whether%20the%20members%20agree%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewith%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fd41586-023-01750-2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edeletion%20of%20the%20periodic%20table%20or%20with%20the%20explanations%20of%20evolution%20and%20electromagnetism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20textbooks%20used%20by%20children%20aged%2014%E2%80%9316%3F%20And%20indeed%20if%20they%20do%2C%20an%20explicit%20stating%20of%20rationale%20and%20an%20ensuing%20debate%20among%20experts%20would%20be%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20NEP%20goal%20of%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecritical%20thinking%20and%20problem%20solving%E2%80%99.%20The%20NCERT%20however%20has%20kept%20it%20simple%20and%20routine.%20T%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20changes%20to%20the%20textbooks%2C%20they%20reiterated%2C%20were%20being%20made%20in%20view%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20and%20to%20%E2%80%9Creduce%20the%20content%20load%E2%80%9D%20on%20students.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20if%20the%20deletion%20is%20prompted%20by%20the%20need%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Elearn%20more%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20precolonial%20history%20of%20science%2C%20does%20this%20entail%20removing%20fundamental%20scientific%20content.%20For%20those%20more%20familiar%20with%20the%20issue%20have%20written%2C%20India%20is%20not%20the%20only%20postcolonial%20country%20grappling%20with%20the%20question%20of%20how%20to%20honour%20and%20recognise%20older%20or%20Indigenous%20forms%20of%20knowledge%20in%20its%20school%20curricula.%20Further%20proven%20efforts%20have%20been%20made%20in%20India%20in%20this%20direction.%20A%20cursory%20look%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncert.nic.in%2Fpdf%2Fnc-framework%2Fnf2005-english.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENational%20Curriculum%20Framework%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ENCF)%202005%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20will%20show%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20May%202023%2C%20several%20topics%20and%20portions%20from%20the%20NCERT%20textbooks%20were%20dropped.%20Certain%20sentences%20on%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20his%20assassin%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20the%20role%20of%20Hindu%20extremists%2C%20the%20Emergency%2C%20the%201984%20anti-Sikh%20riots%20and%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots%2C%20the%20Mughal%20era%2C%20Delhi%20Sultanate%20andthe%20caste%20system%20were%20deleted%20from%20school%20textbooks.%20Questions%20were%20raised%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20%E2%80%98transparency%E2%80%99%20and%20engagement%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20TheNCERT%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20such%20%E2%80%9Cminor%E2%80%9D%20changes%20need%20not%20be%20notified%20as%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cregular%E2%80%9D%20and%20routine%20changes%20are%20not%20notified%20to%20avoid%20%E2%80%9Cany%20confusion%20at%20the%20level%20of%20teachers%20and%20students%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeletions%20of%20%E2%80%98facts%E2%80%99%20such%20as%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassin%20and%20his%20role%20in%20combating%20communal%20frenzy%20are%20therefore%20happenstance%3B%20just%20another%20set%20of%20topics%20in%20the%20syllabus%20that%20can%20be%20omitted%20to%20ease%20the%20burden%20on%20students.%20That%20this%20is%20not%20quite%20true%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20careful%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMqx_y1Lv6qU%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eanalysis%20of%20what%20has%20been%20deleted%20and%20what%20remains.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20dropping%20the%201984%20and%202002%20riots%2C%20there%20are%20two%20messages%3A%20one%2C%20of%20appearing%20even%20handed%20(riots%20have%20been%20dropped%20irrespective%20of%20regimes)%2C%20of%20conveying%20a%20simplified%20and%20faulty%20sense%20of%20%E2%80%98neutrality%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98objectivity%E2%80%99%3B%20and%20two%2C%20of%20presenting%20a%20picture%20of%20an%20idealised%20society%2C%20a%20positive%20picture%20that%20fits%20well%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20triumphant%20nationalism.%20That%20fine%20distinction%20between%20what%20is%20and%20what%20ought%20to%20be%20falls%20outside%20this%20syllabus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fbiology-without-darwin-next-physics-without-newton-and-einstein%5C%22%3EBiology%20Without%20Darwin.%20Next%2C%20Physics%20Without%20Newton%20and%20Einstein%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20matter%20of%20%E2%80%98objectivity%E2%80%99%20rests%20on%20slippery%20terrain.%20I%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3En%20November-December%202020%2C%20a%20controversy%20erupted%20over%20a%20multiple-choice%20question%20in%20the%20Class%2012%20Sociology%20examination%20that%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20unprecedented%20scale%20and%20spread%20of%20anti-Muslim%20violence%20in%20Gujarat%20in%202002%20took%20place%20under%20which%20government%3F%E2%80%9D%20The%20options%20offered%20to%20answer%20this%20question%20were%3A%20%E2%80%9CCongress%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CBJP%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CDemocratic%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CRepublican%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Central%20Board%20of%20School%20Education%20(CBSE)%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cquestion%20was%20inappropriate%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20questions%20should%20be%20academic-oriented%20only%20and%20not%20touch%20upon%20domains%20that%20could%20harm%20sentiments%20of%20people%20based%20on%20social%20and%20political%20choices.%E2%80%9D%20The%20board%20issued%20an%20apology%20and%20action%20was%20to%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20who%20set%20the%20paper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tone%20when%20responding%20to%20the%20NCERT%20deletions%20is%20calm%2C%20reasoned%20and%20practical.%20It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20routine%20functioning%20that%20is%20targeted%20at%20anxious%20parents%2C%20teachers%20and%20students.%20This%20approach%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eworks%20along%20with%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eshrill%20rhetoric%20and%20bombastic%20claims%20of%20the%20current%20regime.%20The%20announcement%20of%20the%2019-member%20high%20powered%20committee%20belongs%20to%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20repertoire%20of%20grandiloquent%20announcements%20in%20consonance%20with%20chest%20thumping%20nationalism.%20It%20is%20the%20awe%20and%20shock%20moment%20addressed%20to%20a%20wider%20public.%20The%20messaging%20is%20to%20silence%20the%20critic%20and%20create%20a%20feel%20good%20factor%20for%20the%20supporter.%20Social%20media%20posts%20suggest%20that%20the%20message%20has%20reached%20for%20whom%20it%20was%20intended.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENine%20years%20is%20a%20long%20time.%20It%20is%20certainly%20long%20enough%20to%20gauge%20the%20cunningness%20of%20a%20regime%20that%20is%20intent%20to%20break%20with%20a%20past%20that%20they%20disdained%20and%20were%20never%20reconciled%20to.%20But%20sans%20state%20power%2C%20one%20that%20they%20had%20to%20live%20with.%20The%20past%20that%20I%20refer%20to%20is%20modern%20India%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20democratic%20ideas%20of%20freedom%20and%20dissent%2C%20equality%20and%20social%20justice%2C%20pluralism%20and%20diversity.%20And%20the%20intent%2C%20however%20faultily%20played%20out%2C%20to%20develop%20a%20spirit%20of%20critical%20enquiry%20seen%20as%20a%20necessary%20enabler%20of%20democracy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20task%20of%20doing%20so%20in%20a%20deeply%20unequal%20society%20was%20not%20easy.%20Given%20the%20embedded%20nature%20of%20rote%20education%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20knowledge%20as%20a%20given%2C%20the%20challenge%20is%20enormous.%20This%20matter%20unfortunately%20did%20not%20receive%20much%20attention.%20The%20NCF%202005%20in%20many%20ways%20was%20an%20exception%2C%20seeking%20as%20it%20did%2C%20to%20encourage%20a%20critical%20perspective%2C%20connect%20the%20lived%20world%20of%20the%20students%20with%C2%A0%20textbooks%20and%20enable%20them%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20the%20links%20between%20the%20self%20and%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20idea%20that%20education%20is%20about%20%E2%80%98facts%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98topics%E2%80%99%20is%20embedded%20in%20society%20and%20remains%20the%20dominant%20view.%20Textbooks%2C%20therefore%2C%20are%20essentially%20about%20content.%20The%20syllabus%20is%20an%20aggregate%20of%20topics.%20Dropping%20evolution%20or%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20is%20just%20about%20reducing%20topics.%20Evaluation%20rests%20on%20the%20ability%20to%20recall%20%E2%80%98facts%E2%80%99%20which%20usually%20means%20events%2C%20definitions%2C%20dates%20and%20names%20associated%20with%20the%20topics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20recalls%20an%20instance%20where%20some%20teachers%20complained%20that%20there%20is%20too%20little%20content%20in%20the%20sociology%20textbooks.%20It%20was%20then%20suggested%20this%20could%20be%20rectified%20by%20adding%20some%20details%20on%20the%20Five%20Year%20Plans.%20%E2%80%98Content%E2%80%99%20would%20thereby%20be%20strengthened.%20Questions%20more%20easily%20formulated.%20Model%20answers%20more%20easily%20prepared.%20There%20is%20a%20practical%20logic%20to%20patterned%20answers.%20Evaluation%20is%20easier.%20It%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20more%20%E2%80%98objective%E2%80%99.%20But%20above%20all%20it%20makes%20learning%2C%20i.e.%20%E2%80%98remembering%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98easy%E2%80%99.%20We%20normally%20do%20not%20discuss%20this%20as%20our%20received%20culture%20of%20knowledge%20wherein%20the%20syllabi%20is%20sacrosanct%3B%20its%20sole%20purpose%20being%20completion%20or%20selectively%20covered%20by%20the%20teacher%20and%20student%20alike%20within%20a%20given%20time%20frame.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20routine%20is%20the%20very%20stuff%20of%20everyday%20practice%20of%20school%20education.%20It%20is%20also%20the%20micro%20level%20context%20within%20which%20teachers%2C%20students%20and%20boards%20operate.%20This%20has%20been%20a%20persistent%20bane%20in%20our%20educational%20system.%20What%20has%20changed%20dramatically%20is%20a%20macro%20context%20wherein%20the%20state%20seeks%20to%20dismantle%20the%20core%20ideas%20of%20equality%2C%20liberty%20and%20fraternity.%20Academic%20freedom%20and%20critical%20education%20is%20being%20systematically%20dismantled%20even%20as%20the%20NEP%20talks%20of%20flexibility%2C%20creativity%20and%20critical%20thinking.%20Indeed%20this%20doublespeak%20is%20a%20hallmark%20of%20the%20current%20regime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMaitrayee%20Chaudhuri%20is%20a%20retired%20professor%20of%20Sociology%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692930647000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F18121235%2FSocial-Science-India-and-the-Contemporary-World-I-class-ix-NCERT.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fthe-rhetoric-routine-and-ruse-of-a-regime-the-case-of-ncert%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20announcement%20of%20the%20new%2019-member%20NCERT%20panel%20needs%20to%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20certain%20approach%20that%20the%20regime%20has%20mastered.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fthe-rhetoric-routine-and-ruse-of-a-regime-the-case-of-ncert%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rolls-Royce%20hit%20fuel%20tanker%20from%20behind%20at%20over%20200%20kmph%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692929675000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103039896%2Cimgsize-616168.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fgurgaon%2Frolls-hit-fuel-tanker-from-behind-at-over-200-kmph%2Farticleshow%2F103038953.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rampreet%20is%20unlikely%20to%20have%20known%20what%20hit%20him.%20The%20diesel%20tanker%20he%20was%20driving%20juddered%2C%20lurched%20and%20flipped%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye%2C%20killing%20him%20and%20his%20co-driver%20on%20the%20spot.%22%2C%22author%22%3