1%20charges%20for%20a%20total%20of%2019%20defendants%2C%20and%20because%20the%20district%20attorney%20has%20brought%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-rico-charge-meaning-racketeering-definition-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERICO%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20trial%20will%20be%20lengthy%2C%20Redmon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20RICO%20case%20often%20involves%20presenting%20information%20that%20may%20not%20be%20immediately%20relevant%20to%20a%20particular%20defendant%20on%20trial%20but%20relevant%20to%20%26quot%3Bestablishing%20the%20overt%20acts%20of%20the%20conspiracy%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20more%20witnesses%20and%2C%20thus%2C%20a%20longer%20trial%2C%20the%20professor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20case%20is%20also%20politically%20sensitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20and%20lawyers%20will%20have%20to%20ask%20potential%20jurors%20if%20they%20can%20hear%20a%20case%20impartially%20despite%20their%20personal%20beliefs%20or%20political%20leanings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20trial%20against%20Young%20Thug%2C%20one%20woman%20was%20asked%20if%20she%20was%20familiar%20with%20the%20rapper%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F20%2Fus%2Ftrump-young-thug-rico.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20woman%20said%20she%20knew%20Young%20Thug%20and%20would%20make%20sitting%20in%20on%20the%20case%20%26quot%3Bsurreal%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20she%20would%20be%20fair%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20jurors%20will%20be%20questioned%20about%20their%20political%20beliefs%20and%20if%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20put%20that%20aside%20in%20the%20Trump%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20lawyers%20can%20object%20to%20a%20juror%20just%20because%20they%20are%20a%20registered%20Democrat%20or%20Republican%2C%20Redmon%20said.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20a%20court%20wouldn't%20have%20any%20viable%20jurors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20to%20be%20a%20prejudice%20or%20bias%20that's%20so%20fixed%20that%20it%20would%20impact%20their%20ability%20to%20judge%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20witnesses%20and%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20evidence%20being%20presented%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjury-selection-election-interference-case-georgia-fulton-county-donald-trump-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692927621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e7da1c52bc2d001991bd8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjury-selection-election-interference-case-georgia-fulton-county-donald-trump-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fulton%20County%20courthouse%20has%20sifted%20through%20more%20than%202%2C000%20potential%20jurors%20for%20Young%20Thug's%20trial.%20Juror%20selection%20will%20also%20be%20hard%20for%20the%20Trump%20case%2C%20law%20professor%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjury-selection-election-interference-case-georgia-fulton-county-donald-trump-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan%20is%20next%20country%20to%20shoot%20for%20Moon%20after%20India%20and%20Russia%20missions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692926850000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F25%2Ffull%2F1692926384-3271.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapan-is-next-country-to-shoot-for-moon-after-india-and-russia-missions-123082500114_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Japanese%20entrepreneurs%20try%20to%20build%20their%20space%20startups%2C%20the