lliance%20is%20a%20national-level%20alliance%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20AAP%20trying%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%93%20where%20polls%20are%20due%20this%20year%20%E2%80%93%20the%20party%20said%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20only%20for%20the%20national-level%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20intelligent%20enough%20to%20see%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20state%20election%20where%20the%20issues%20are%20electricity%2C%20water%2C%20roads%2C%20jobs%2C%20and%20the%20national%20election%20where%20the%20issue%20is%20the%20economy%2C%20assault%20on%20the%20constitution%2C%20federalism%2C%20etc.%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Marathe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20(INDIA)%20alliance%20is%20for%20the%20national%20election.%20For%20the%20state%20elections%2C%20AAP%20has%20a%20viable%20model.%20The%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20model%20has%20found%20resonance%20across%20the%20country%20including%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20coalitions%20like%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20past%20despite%20back%20and%20forth%20%5Bdisagreements%5D%20and%20political%20bickering%20between%20constituent%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20fine%20example%20of%20a%20coalition%20alliance%20that%20works%2C%20which%20was%20in%202004%2C%20when%20a%20stable%20government%20got%20over%208%25%20growth%2C%20a%20number%20of%20pro-poor%20reforms%20including%20MGNREGA%20that%20came%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20rescue%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20a%20number%20of%20far-reaching%20reforms%2C%20a%20robust%20growth%20rate%20was%20brought%20during%20an%20alliance%20and%20that%20did%20not%20stop%20bickerings%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Avijit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20keeps%20the%20alliance%20going%20is%20a%20common%20minimum%20programme.%20Politics%20goes%20on.%20After%20all%20you%E2%80%99re%20in%20politics%2C%20things%20are%20misunderstood%20and%20things%20are%20said%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20fine.%20But%20that%20has%20no%20bearing%20on%20the%20solid%20alliance%20that%20has%20got%20together%20%E2%80%93%20an%20anti-BJP%20alliance%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20against%20the%20BJP%20dividing%20the%20country%20and%20destroying%20the%20economy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvijit%20said%20that%20the%20meeting%20which%20Lamba%20referred%20to%20was%20not%20about%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20working%20in%20any%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20focus%20is%20on%20a%20very%20strong%20INDIA%20alliance%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20other%20things%20will%20be%20worked%20out.%20It%20is%20an%20ongoing%20process.%20When%20you%20form%20unity%2C%20it%20is%20always%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20in%20meetings%20where%20those%20comments%20were%20made%2C%20those%20were%20purely%20%5Bmade%5D%20to%20evaluate%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20its%20workers%20in%20Delhi%3B%20it%20was%20not%20about%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20%E2%80%98compromise%E2%80%99%20on%20state%20elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20AAP%20leader%2C%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20does%20not%20imply%20that%20parties%20should%20compromise%20on%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20say%20that%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20must%20compromise%20on%20state%20elections%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20that%20was%20ever%20intended%20to%20be%20the%20consequence%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20different%20kinds%20of%20states%20%E2%80%93%20states%20where%20there%20are%20existing%20alliances%2C%20so%20it%20is%20up%20to%20those%20parties%20to%20decide%20how%20they%20will%20go%20ahead.%20I%20cannot%20imagine%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20fighting%20state%20elections%20with%20the%20Congress%20as%20an%20alliance%20partner%2C%20or%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%20tying%20up%20for%20the%20state%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20alliance%20is%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20that%20is%20why%20this%20alliance%20has%20come%20together%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that%20there%20is%20that%20level%20of%20clarity%20on%20all%20sides%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20leader%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Avijit%20said%20that%20the%20exact%20strategy%20cannot%20be%20preempted%20at%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20not%20preempt%20any%20strategy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20unity%20formed%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months%E2%80%A6%20the%20modalities%20of%20the%20unity%20are%20being%20worked%20out%20as%20it%20always%20is.%20The%20common%20minimum%20programme%20is%20already%20there%20to%20counter%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-narendra-modi-nervous%5C%22%3EHas%20the%20India%20Alliance%20Made%20PM%20Modi%20Nervous%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETriangular%20contests%20in%20state%20elections%20to%20help%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20concerns%20have%20been%20raised%20that%20a%20three-corner%20fight%20between%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20AAP%20in%20the%20upcoming%20state%20assembly%20elections%20could%20end%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-aap-congress-gujarat-bugbear%5C%22%3Ehelping%20the%20BJP%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20it%20did%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20assembly%20elections%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20unfair%20to%20say%20that%20AAP%20takes%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20votes.%20AAP%20takes%20anti-incumbency%20votes%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Marathe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20state%20like%20Chhattisgarh%20or%20Rajasthan%20where%20the%20Congress%20is%20in%20power%2C%20AAP%20will%20take%20votes%20from%20those%20who%20are%20disenchanted%20with%20the%20government%20and%20those%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20BJP%20either.%20So%20to%20say%20that%20AAP%20only%20takes%20one%20party%E2%80%99s%20vote%20is%20not%20fair%20and%20not%20true.%20If%20you%20see%20the%20election%20data%20for%20Delhi%20in%202020%20and%202015%2C%20vote%20share%20shows%20supporters%20of%20every%20party%20have%20voted%20for%20AAP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvijit%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20a%20three-corner%20fight%20as%20the%20Congress%20will%20win%20all%20three%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20winning%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Verma%2C%20fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%2C%20and%20Visiting%20Assistant%20Professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Political%20Science%2C%20Ashoka%20University%2C%20said%20that%20in%20the%20three%20states%20where%20elections%20are%20due%20this%20year%2C%20a%20triangular%20contest%20is%20unlikely%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20not%20be%20a%20three-corner%20fight%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20bipolar%20fight%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20AAP%20has%20any%20traction%20as%20of%20now.%20They%20might%20have%202-3%25%20votes%20but%20at%20this%20moment%20it%20does%20not%20look%20like%20AAP%20has%20any%20traction%20to%20make%20it%20a%20triangular%20contest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVerma%20said%20that%20while%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20AAP%20may%20have%20gained%20from%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20votes%2C%20every%20state%20is%20a%20different%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChhattisgarh%20is%20a%20difficult%20state%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20state%20elections.%20Even%20with%20AAP%20contesting%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20easy%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20win%20Chhattisgarh.%20Every%20state%20is%20different.%20In%20Punjab%2C%20AAP%20has%20a%20big%20presence.%20First%20four%20MPs%20from%20AAP%20in%202014%20came%20from%20Punjab%20before%20they%20even%20had%20MPs%20in%20Delhi.%20In%20the%202017%20Punjab%20elections%2C%20AAP%20came%20close%20to%20winning.%20Their%20win%20in%202022%20is%20a%20fruition%20of%20eight%20years%20of%20assault.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Gujarat%2C%20yes%2C%20they%20did%20get%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20votes.%20But%20Congress%20has%20been%20a%20party%20that%20has%20not%20been%20in%20power%20in%20Gujarat%20for%2025%20years%2C%20so%20it%20is%20natural%20for%20Congress%20voters%20to%20think%20let%E2%80%99s%20try%20something%20else.%20But%20that%20is%20not%20the%20case%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20Both%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20in%20power.%20So%20for%20voters%20to%20think%20of%20a%20third%20alternative%2C%20which%20may%20not%20form%20the%20government%20but%20will%20just%20play%20a%20spoiler%2C%20is%20unlikely%20and%20for%20the%20AAP%20to%20play%20a%20role%20in%20these%20three%20states%20is%20difficult%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692896486000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F18164404%2Fcongress-aap.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famid-disagreements-over-state-polls-congress-and-aap-say-india-alliance-is-for-national-election%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20parties%20have%20said%20that%20the%20alliance%2C%20which%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20remains%20'robust'%20and%20has%20been%20formed%20for%20the%20'national%20stage'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22en