ia.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-1692620841-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327817%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2017%2C%20Gautam%20discovered%20his%20sexuality.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20these%20sessions%20that%20the%20counsellor%20suggested%20that%20Gautam%20be%20tested%20for%20HIV%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20multiple%20sexual%20partners.%20And%20though%20he%20had%20no%20symptoms%2C%20he%20tested%20positive%20in%202009.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20today%2C%20when%20people%20come%20to%20know%20that%20they%20are%20positive%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20comes%20to%20their%20mind%20is%20how%20long%20they%20are%20going%20to%20live.%20I%20also%20did%20not%20know%20how%20long%20I%20would%20survive.%20Questions%20like%20%E2%80%98Who%20will%20take%20care%20of%20my%20parents%20after%20my%20death%3F%E2%80%99%20started%20worrying%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20it%20took%20him%20a%20year%20to%20understand%20that%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20worry.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20upset%20and%20depressed%20in%20that%20period%2C%20but%20my%20fear%20went%20away%20when%20I%20started%20meeting%20people%20who%20are%20HIV-positive.%20They%20made%20me%20understand%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20worry%20if%20I%20took%20medicines%20on%20time.%20Treatment%20adherence%20is%20important%20to%20lead%20a%20normal%20life.%20Today%2C%20I%20do%20not%20even%20feel%20that%20I%20am%20positive.%20It%20hardly%20matters%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20as%20he%20was%20still%20accepting%20the%20reality%2C%20Gautam%20was%20not%20spared%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F97559%2Fhiv-aids-act-positive-news-legislation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estigma%20and%20d