1200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327623%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20has%20introduced%20a%20number%20of%20interventions%2C%20including%20teaching%20children%20the%20NCERT%20syllabus%20via%20animations%20and%20fun%20videos.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20on%20digital%20inclusion.%20Our%20focus%20is%20that%20every%20child%20should%20have%20digital%20%3Cem%3Eshiksha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(education)%20as%20technology%20is%20our%20future.%20If%20these%20students%20do%20not%20adapt%20to%20digital%20methods%2C%20chances%20are%20that%20they%20miss%20out%20on%20good%20opportunities.%20With%20Muskaan%20Dreams%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20bring%20smiles%20to%20these%20children%20and%20help%20them%20fulfil%20their%20dreams%20of%20a%20better%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2031-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202017%2C%20the%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government%20schools%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98When%20I%20took%20a%20stand%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20farmer%20family%20in%20rural%20Gwalior%2C%20Abhishek%20developed%20an%20interest%20in%20teaching%20underprivileged%20children%20during%20his%20college%20days.%20In%202013%2C%20while%20studying%20engineering%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20he%20started%20devoting%20his%20weekends%20to%20teaching%20children%20in%20government-run%20shelter%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20saw%20one%20of%20my%20classmates%20going%20to%20teach%20students%20in%20shelter%20homes.%20I%20went%20along%20with%20her%20and%20saw%20how%20such%20children%20are%20deprived%20of%20education.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20children%20of%20single%20parents%20and%20from%20tribal%20or%20rural%20backgrounds.%20Coming%20from%20a%20rural%20background%2C%20I%20started%20connecting%20with%20them%20and%20I%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20teach%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20two%20years%2C%20they%20formed%20a%20group%20of%20200%20volunteers%20and%20expanded%20their%20reach%20to%20Bhopal%20and%20Indore%20as%20well.%20By%20now%2C%20this%20was%20no%20more%20a%20weekend%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20NGO%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20one%20lakh%20students%20and%20is%20making%20learning%20in%20government%20schools%20fun.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327624%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20NGO%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20one%20lakh%20students%20and%20is%20making%20learning%20in%20government%20schools%20fun.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%20after%20he%20graduated%2C%20Abhishek%20wanted%20to%20completely%20dedicate%20himself%20to%20teaching%20children.%20The%20decision%20was%20not%20welcomed%20by%20his%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%2C%20who%20is%20a%20government%20officer%2C%20was%20completely%20against%20the%20decision.%20He%20asked%20me%20to%20get%20a%20good%20job%20and%20drop%20the%20idea.%20But%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20quit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20studied%20in%20a%20government%20school%2C%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20ignore%20the%20challenges%20he%20needed%20to%20address.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20idea%20was%20to%20improve%20the%20learning%20experience%20of%20children%20so%20that%20when%20they%20enter%20the%20classrooms%2C%20their%20interest%20increases%20and%20they%20come%20to%20school%20every%20day.%20We%20already%20know%20that%20the%20dropout%20rate%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20challenges%20faced%20by%20government%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20education%20in%20the%20government%20school%20because%20when%20they%20are%20educated%20there%20in%20a%20better%20way%20they%20would%20not%20require%20tutoring.%20But%20my%20father%20was%20so%20angry%20at%20my%20decision%20that%20he%20stopped%20speaking%20to%20me.%20If%20I%20would%20be%20in%20the%20bedroom%2C%20he%20would%20move%20to%20the%20drawing-room%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20continued%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20that%20no%20one%20should%20quit%20on%20their%20dreams.%20Dreams%20have%20the%20power%20to%20become%20reality.%20This%20kept%20me%20motivated%20when%20my%20father%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20me.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20took%20a%20stand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20today%2C%20he%20is%20proud%20of%20the%20work%20I%20do.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20we%20invited%20former%20vice%20president%20M%20Venkaiah%20Naidu%20for%20a%20project%20launch%2C%20my%20father%20also%20joined%20us%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20He%20understood%20that%20I%20was%20serious%20about%20the%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327625%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government%20schools.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20the%20govt%20school%20ecosystem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20launching%20the%20non-profit%2C%20Abhishek%20started%20his%20journey%20with%20a%20government%20school%20for%20girls.%20Talking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%20in%202017%2C%20there%