0hard%20to%20develop%20technologies%20for%20agricultural%20advancements%20at%20home.%20However%2C%20India%20did%20not%20have%20%5Ban%20indigenous%5D%20hydroponics%20technology.%20While%20there%20are%20startups%20that%20are%20using%20hydroponics%2C%20they%20are%20mostly%20exported%20by%20Israel%20or%20Japan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIncreasing%20the%20food%20productivity%20of%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20student%20and%20a%20university%20faculty%20member%2C%20Dr%20Sethi%20has%20dedicated%20nearly%20three%20decades%20of%20his%20life%20to%20researching%20and%20developing%20sustainable%20technologies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20technology%20claims%20to%20save%2090%20percent%20of%20water%20through%20recirculation%20mode.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327481%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20technology%20claims%20to%20save%2090%20percent%20of%20water%20through%20recirculation%20mode.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20V%20P%20Sethi%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20spending%20five%20years%20on%20research%20and%20development%20with%20a%20very%20small%20team%20of%20scholars%20and%20scientists%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Botany%2C%20Chemistry%2C%20Soil%20and%20Vegetable%20Sciences%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20crack%20the%20code.%20Using%20HHT%20helps%20in%20improved%20water%20and%20nutrient%20perforation%20and%20re-circulation%20systems%20for%20pot-based%20substrate%20hydroponics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201968%20in%20Ludhiana%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Dr%20Sethi%20did%20his%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20in%20Agriculture%20Engineering%20and%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20Mechanical%20Engineering.%20It%20was%20during%20his%20postdoctoral%20fellowship%20in%20the%20US%20that%20Dr%20Sethi%20met%20with%20a%20Korean%20professor%20Dr%20Chiwong%20Lee%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20field%20of%20developing%20hydroponics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20working%20on%20the%20various%20substrates%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298712%2Fiim-graduate-citygreens-hydroponics-startup-trains-farmers-increase-earnings%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20used%20in%20hydroponics%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20found%20it%20very%20intriguing.%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20back%20to%20India%20and%20develop%20our%20own%20hydroponics%20system.%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20university%20and%20told%20them%20about%20my%20idea%20of%20developing%20a%20Hybrid%20Hydroponics%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Dr%20Sethi%20nearly%20five%20years%20to%20fully%20develop%20the%20HHT%20system%20and%20grow%20vegetables%20using%20it%2C%20and%20another%20five%20to%20get%20the%20patent%20rights%2C%20which%20he%20and%20PAU%20received%20in%20November%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20HHT%20and%20how%20does%20it%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20types%20of%20hydroponics%20%E2%80%94%20water-based%20and%20substrate-based.%20Dr%20Sethi%E2%80%99s%20hybrid%20technology%20merges%20the%20two%20to%20use%20the%20best%20of%20both%20technologies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20seed%20money%20of%20Rs%205%2C00%2C000%20from%20the%20university%2C%20I%20started%20my%20research%20on%20developing%20the%20technology.%20We%20developed%20a%20small%20greenhouse%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20250%20plants.%20It%20took%20me%20nearly%20two%20years%20to%20fully%20develop%20the%20technology%20and%20I%20tested%20it%20for%20another%20three%20years%20before%20applying%20for%20a%20patent%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20took%20a%20few%20hits%20and%20misses%20to%20become%20what%20it%20is%20today%2C%20notes%20Dr%20Sethi.%20While%20the%20concept%20of%20soil-less%20farming%20is%20not%20unknown%20to%20us%2C%20what%20he%20noticed%20was%20that%20the%20technology%20uses%20water%20from%20reservoirs%20and%20passes%20it%20to%20the%20pots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20that%20was%20not%20taken%20by%20the%20plants%20would%20go%20to%20waste.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Hybrid%20Hydroponics%20Technology%2C%20we%20save%20this%20water%20by%20using%20the%20technique%20of%20recirculation.%20We%20developed%20a%20porous%20plate%20between%20the%20pots.%20The%20lower%20part%20of%20the%20pot%20contains%20the%20shallow%20water%20pond%20and%20the%20upper%20part%20of%20the%20pot%20carries%20the%20substrate.%20The%20plate%20between%20the%20two%20is%20the%20innovation%20as%20it%20carries%20equivalent%20pressure%20at%20both%20the%20upper%20and%20lower%20end%20of%20the%20pot.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20allows%20the%20roots%20to%20breathe%20and%20grow%2C%20and%20from%20the%20top%2C%20they%20would%20get%20ample%20oxygen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20recirculation%20mode%2C%20we%20could%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247233%2Fbori-bandh-c