ing%20the%20campaign%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Himanshu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20feels%20that%20this%20work%20is%20also%20part%20of%20his%20duty.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20reunite%20these%20children%20with%20their%20families%2C%20then%20I%20do%20not%20think%20we%20are%20doing%20a%20good%20job.%20What%20we%20do%20is%20just%20part%20of%20my%20legal%20responsibilities.%20There%20have%20been%20moments%20when%20we%20see%20families%20crying%20with%20happiness%20when%20their%20kids%20reach%20home.%20Looking%20at%20their%20smiles%20makes%20your%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu.%20All%20photos%3A%20Saurabh%20Maurya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691761928000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-4-1691757772.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327071%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IAS%20officer%20Himanshu%20Nagpal%20spearheads%20Mission%20Muskaan%20to%20reunite%20lost%20children%20living%20in%20Varanasi%E2%80%99s%20ghats%2C%20railway%20stations%2C%20and%20temples%20with%20their%20families%20across%20India.%20He%20shares%20how%20he%20does%20this.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327071%2Fvaranasi-ias-officer-himanshu-nagpal-mission-muskaan-reunites-lost-children-with-families%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Southern%20Airways%20Express%20Is%20Suing%20Former%20Pilots%20For%20Training%20Costs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20Florida-based%20company%20is%20trying%20to%20enforce%20a%20controversial%20employment%20clause%20that%20has%20gained%20national%20attention%20recently.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691090145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F64cbe7cf2000005e00f83977.jpeg%3Fops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22